TE7 2 CHIUNN
TI7 KOAN5 CHHIU7-TENG2 CHOE3 KANG E5 LANG5

몮Ti7 koan5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang몯 che si7 put-kho2-su-gi7 e5 ki7-sut8, si7 bo5 peng5-siong5, si7 boe7 thang pi2-pheng7 e5 ki7-sut8. Ti7 Thai3-peng5-iuN5 hai3-hoaN7 e5 sou2-chai7, u7 chit8 koa2 bo5 hoan5 bo5 lo2 e5 chho3-chha5 kang-lang5. Ti7 in e5 jin5-seng tiong u7 chit8-hang7 hou7 in choat8-tui3 boe7 tang3 boe7-ki3-tit e5 keng-giam7, chiu7-si7 in teh khoaN3 hit e5 ti7 koan5 e5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang e5 lang5 e5 si5, in khoaN3-kiN3 hit lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 bo5 teh chu3-i3, bo5 sin5-keng, bo5 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 chong7-thai7, ti7 toe7-bin7 kap khong-tiong teh kang-chok e5 si5, in the3 hit lang5 chin kiaN, kiaN kau3 khi2-tio5 khi2-lai5.

Cheng5 chit8 jit8 sou2 keng2-tioh8 e5 toa7-chhiu7 si7 ---- 300 chhioh koan5 e5 To5-kek-lah-su chong-chhiu7, chhiu7-thau5 e5 tit8-keng3 u7 5 chhioh, tit8 chhun kau3 chhiu7-teng2, chit khoan2 chhiu7 ti7 Eng-siok8 e5 Ko-lun7-pi2-a siong5-siong5 u7 khoaN3-tioh8.

U7 chit8 e5 tai7-iok 19 hoe3 e5 chheng-lian5, si7 choan-bun5 choe3 chit khoan2 e5 kang e5, chiu7-si7 peh-chiuN7 hiah-nih8 koan5 e5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang. Chi3-chio2 ti7 hit jit8 i si7 chin khoai3-lok8, bin7-mau7 u7 an-choan5 tho3-tong3. I2-keng kui2 na7 le2-pai3-ku2 siu7 tek8-piat8 e5 hun3-lian7 liau2-au7, chiu7 chiaN5-choe3 chit e5 hai2-hoaN7, te7-it gau5 ti7 koan5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang e5 lang5. Hit jit8 i e5 kha, chheng7 u7 thih-teng e5 oe5, koh toa3 soh, pak8 ti7 io-nih, chiu7 thiau3 chiuN7 chhiu7 e5 tiong-kut, ti7 te7-bin7 chit8 toa7 kun5 chho3-chha5 kang-lang5 iau2-boe7 kam2-kak e5 si5, i chhin-chhiuN7 phong3-chhi2 chit8-poaN7-iuN7 peh-chiuN7 50 chhioh koan5 e5 sou2-chai7 lah, i chiong soh hiat chiuN7 koan5, pak8 ho2-se3, chiong thih-teng-oe5 chhah ti7 chhiu7 e5 tiong-kut, thau5-khak kiah8 koan5, chit8-pou7 chit8-pou7 peh-chiuN7 koan5 khi3, i e5 sin-the2 i2-keng chun2-pi7 beh eng3-hu3 it-chhe3 e5 tong7-chok.

Tit8-tit8 peh, koan5 koh-khah koan5, i it-tit8 peh khi2 khi3, in-ui7 i e5 tong7-chok, chhiu7-teng2 chiu7 cheng5-au7 it-tit8 io5-tang7. E7-bin7 e5 lang5 chiong in e5 sin-the2 hiaN3 au7, thau5-khak ng3 teng2-bin7 khoaN3 chiuN7 koan5 khi3, keng-koe3 hiah-nih8 ku2 e5 si5-kan, in e5 am7-kun2 chiu7 sng koh thiaN3, bak8-chiu khoaN3 siuN ku2 ia7 soa3 bu7 khi3. Tui3 tak8 sou2-chai7 long2 oe7-thang thiaN-tioh8 hoaN-hi2 kap o-lo2 hoah kio3 e5 siaN teh kou2-bu2 i, jiat8-seng5 e5 siaN2-im ng3 khong-tiong thoan5 chiuN7-khi3, i ti7 chhiu7-teng2 chin lou2-lek8 kang-chok, chin7 i sou2 oe7 ti7 hia choe3-kang.

Hian7-chai7 i theng5-kha lah, hit sou2-chai7 koan5 u7 200 chhioh! Sit8-chai7 u7 kau3-giah8 koan5, i chiu7 khai-si2 kang-chok lah, chiong pou2-thau5 theh8 chhut lai5, khai-si2 chho3 chha5, chiong chhiu7 e5 chiu-ui5 tit8-phut. I e5 sin-the2 hiong3 au7-bin7 jian5-au7 eng7-lat8 phut loh8-khi3, siang7-si5 chha5-iu3 chhin-chhiuN7 hou7, loh8 ti7 e7-bin7 hiah e5 chho3-chha5 kang-lang5 hia. Teh chho3 e5 si5 u7 2 hang7 su7 i tioh8 chin chu3-i3, che 2 hang7 su7 chin u7 kho2-leng5 hoat-seng gui5-hiam2, i tek-khak tioh8 chin7-liong7 siam2-pi7 chiah e5 gui5-hiam2. Thau5 chit8-hang7 chiu7-si7 teh chho3 e5 si5 tioh8 chin se3-ji7, na7 chho3 m7-tioh8 sou2-chai7, chho3 tioh8 pak8 i e5 sin-khu e5 soh, an2-ni it-chhe3 chiu7 oan5 lah. Chit-hang7 su7 ti7 kui2 na7 le2-pai3 cheng5 ti7 Un-ko-hoa5-to2 u7 hoat-seng, chit8 e5 kang-lang5 bo5 chu3-i3 loan7-phut, i chhui3 kou5-kou5 e5 sin-the2 hou7 lang5 bai5-chong3 ti7 chhiu7-kha. Koh chit8 hang7 chiu7-si7 i chho3-chhiu7 e5 si5, tioh8 chho3 ho2-se3, na7 bo5, chhiu7 oe7 to2 tui3 i chit peng5 lai5, chiong i e5 sin-khu phoa3 choe3 2 te3, chit khoan2 e5 su7 ia7 hoat-seng koe3.

Na7-si7 chit-e5 chheng-lian5 lang5, si7 chin oe7 hiau2 po2-siu2 i ka-ki7, sou2-i2 it-chhe3 e5 keng-koe3 long2 chin sun7-li7. Chhiu7 teng2 hit pou7-hun7 siu7 chho3 loh8-lai5, i kio3 hiah e5 ti7 e7-bin7 e5 kang-lang5 long2 tioh8 chau2. Chit si5 i oe7 tu2-tioh8 chin gui5-hiam2, chiu7-si7 chhiu7 e5 teng2 pou7-hun7 teh beh tng7 e5 si5, chhiu7 oe7 cheng5-au7 io5 kau3 chin li7-hai7, io5 e5 khoah u7 15-20 chhioh. Hit si5 tioh8 oe7-hiau2 sun7-se3 kap chhiu7 saN-kap choe3-hoe2 io5, na7 bo5, bin7 chiu7 oe7 hou7 chhiu7 kong3-tioh8, chiu7 piN3 choe3 bah-chiuN3. U7 chin choe7 ti7 koan5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang e5 lang5, in e5 bin7 long2 hou7 chhiu7 phah kau3 piN3 bah-chiuN3, in-ui7 in iau2 boe7 kap chhiu7 saN-kap tin2-tang7 e5 si5, hiah toa7 e5 chhiu7 chit8-pai2 koh chit8-pai2 phah to3-tng2-lai5, bin7 siu7-phah kau3 hui-siong5 li7-hai7.

Hut-jian5-kan i theng5-chi2 it-chhe3 e5 kang-chok, si7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3? In khoaN3-kiN3 i thau2-khui pak8 ti7 io e5 soh, koaN2-kin2 thoa-khui i e5 thih-teng-oe5, liu loh8-khi3 iok u7 12 chhioh e5 sou2-chai7 beh siam2-pi7 chhiu7 to2 loh8-lai5. Au7-lai5 koh chiong thih-teng-oe5 teng3 ti7 chhiu7 e5 tiong-kut, chiong i e5 soh pak8 ho2, koh pak8-an5 i e5 kha, teh theng3-hau7. Bo5 ku2 chhiu7 e5 teng2 pou7-bun7 100 chhioh chiu7 tng7, tui7-loh8 toe2. In khoaN3-kiN3 i kap chhiu7 cheng5-au7 teh io5-tang7, i lian5 chit8-sut-a2 to bo5 tin2-tang7, chhin-chhiuN7 tang5-siong7, bo5 sin5-keng, bo5 khui3-lat8 ku3-chai7 chhiu7 teh io5, tit8-kau3 chhiu7 e5 io5-tang7 oan5-choan5 theng5.

Jian5-au7, i chiu7 chiau3 몮ti7 koan5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang e5 lang5몯 e5 kui-ki2, khai-si2 i e5 kang-chok, chiu7-si7 tioh8 khan kng3-soh ti7 chhiu7-teng2, hit e5 kng3-soh tang7 u7 400 kin, sou2-i2 tioh8 eng7 thih-kau giu2, lai5 tiau3 ti7 chhiu7-teng2, chit-e5 u7 1 chhun3 chhou e5 kng3-soh, tui3 chit chang5 chhiu7 tioh8 khan kau3 leng7-goa7 chit8 chang5 chhiu7-teng2, si7 beh eng7 chit-tiau5 e5 kng3-soh lai5 un7-poaN toa7 koh chhou e5 sam-khou.

Hian7-chai7, i sou2 chho3 loh8-lai5 e5 chhiu7 hit sou2-chai7 e5 tit8-keng3 tu2-ho2 2 chhioh, i theng5-khun3, in teh theng3-hau7, in kam2-kak chin ki5-koai3 si7 bin5-bang7 tioh8 mah? In e5 bak8-chiu si7 hou7 i phian3 khi3? Bo5, i e5 sin-khu theng5 ti7 poaN3 khong-tiongm khia7 ti7 chiu-ui5 chhioh khoah e5 chhiu7 e5 tiong-kut, li7 in e5 thau5-khak teng2-bin7 200 chhioh koan5 e5 sou2-chai7.

Ng3 teng2-bin7 teh khoaN3 e5 chho3-chha5 kang-lang5 e5 tiong-kan u7 tiap-a2-ku2 e5 an-cheng7, in chu3-i3 teh khoaN3 hit e5 iong2-kam2 ti7 koan5 chhiu7-teng2 choe3-kang e5 lang5, cheng7-kau3 long2 bo5 siaN-se3, choe7-choe7 lang5 e5 sim-chong7 chit8 si5 thiau3 kau3 chin li7-hai7. In it-tit8 khia7 ti7 hia, chhin3-koaN7 tit8-tit8 piaN3 chhut-lai5, hou7 in kam2-kak kui seng-khu long2 bo5 lat8, chong2-si7 chhiu7-teng2 e5 kang-chok si7 hiah-nih8 u7 khip-in2-lat8, in boe7-tang3 bo5 khoaN3 i e5 kang-chok.

I khia7 ti7 chheN-chheN e5 khong-tiong-nih8, oe7 lian3 loh8-lai5 boe7? I kiam2 oe7 tang3 hiah-nih8 ku2 khia7 ti7 hia mah? Hian7-chai7 i e5 po2-thau5, tui3 i sou2 khia7 e5 sou2-chai7 hiat tui3 3 chhioh koan5 e5 sou2-chai7 khi3, tau3-ti2 i si7 beh choe3 sim2-mih8?

Chong2-si7 li2 khoaN3! Po2-thau5 ka-lauh8 loh8-lai5, chhiu7-ki at-chih8, lak loh8 toe7, i oan-io, teh khoaN3 e5 lang5 long2 m7-kaN2 chhoan2-khui3 eng7 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 bak8-chiu chu3-i3 teh khoaN3, i e5 sin-the2 ban7-ban7 hoe5-hok8 an-teng7, 5 hun cheng au7, koh chai3 khia7 ti7 toe7-bin7 lah. Sui5-si5 u7 toa7 o-lo2 e5 siaN tui3 chin heng-hun3 e5 chho3-chha5 kang-lang5 tiong hoat-chhut-lai5, ia7 tai7-ke chiong i pau-ui5 khi2-lai5.

몮Ti7 koan5 chhiu7-eng2 cho3-kang e5 lang5,몯 tit-tioh8 cheng3-lang5 e5 o-lo2 kap him-soan7.

Hit me5 i khun3 boe7 khi3, si5-kan tit8-tit8 beh koe3 khi3, na7-si7 i ti7 chhng5-nih8 hoan-lai5 hoan-khi3, boe7 tit-tioh8 hioh-khun3. Koe3-khi3 e5 tai7-chi3 chit8-bou5 koh chit8-bou5 chhut-hian7 ti7 i e5 bin7-cheng5. I e5 chhu3 lau7-bu2, siau3-lain5 si5-tai7 e5 tang5-phoaN7, i2-kip ki5-tha chiong2-chong2 sin5-seng3 e5 ki3-ek8 chhiong-moa2 ti7 hun7-loan7 e5 thau5-nau2 lai7.

I hoah kong2: 몮An2-ni beh an2-choaN2, sim2-mih8 tai7 chi3 hou7 goa2 kui mi5 chiah-nih8 kan-khou2?몯

