Si7 chit8 e5 geh8-kng-me5, toa7 koh tng5 e5 chhiu7-iaN2 chin chheng-chho2 chio3 kau3 toe7-chiuN7, chin hng7 sou2-chai7, mui2 chit8-tong3 chhu3, long2 oe7 khoaN3 kau3 chin beng5, bo5 chit8 e5 siaN-im teh kiau2-jiau2 am3-me5 e5 thiam7-cheng7, lian5 hiah-nih8 toa7 e5 chhiu7-na5 pun2 sin ia7 ti7 an-bin5 tiong.

