Lun7 kau3 goa2 e5 kok-ka Ka-na2-tai7, ti7 toe7-tou5 put-ko3 chiam3 chit8-sut-sut-a2 na7-tiaN7. Siat-su2 Tai7-se-iuN5 kap Thai3-peng5-iuN5 e5 hai2-chui2, na7 ti7 chit8-me5 e5 tiong-kan tiong3 khi2-lai5, im-moa2 choan5-pou7 e5 Ka-na2-tai7, goa2 siong-sin3 ti7 keh-jit8 cha2-khi2, Bi2-kok e5 po3-choa2 it-teng7 u7 chin choe7 po3 kong2, 몮Cha-me5 Ka-na2-tai7 i2-keng tui3 se3-kai3 e5 tiong-kan siau-biat8 lah.몯 Na7 eng7 sou3-bak8 lai5 sng3, lan2 boe7-tang3 sng3 choe3 sim2-mih8. Lan2 ki3-jian5 si7 an2-ni, siaN2-su7 ka-ki7 teh siuN7, 몮goan2 si7 chia e5 peh-siN3몯 neh? SiaN2-su7 siuN7 lan2 si7 pi2 se3-kai3 ki5-thaN sou2-chai7 e5 lang5 koh khah iau3-kin2 nih? SiaN2-su7 Siong7-te3 it-teng7 tioh8 pi2 pat8-lang5 khah koan-sim lan2 nih? I ai3 lan2 u7 se3-kai3 e5 iN7-siong7, an2-ni lan2 chiu7 thang ui7-tioh8 choan5 se3-kai3 lai5 choe3 thoan5 hok-im e5 kang-chok. Ki-tok si7 ui7-tioh8 se3-kai3 lai5 si2 e5, lan2 na7 u7 tui3 choan5 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 e5 iN7-siong7, lan2 chiu7 oe7 thang khoaN3-kiN3, I sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 se3-kai3 lah.

CHI3-SIONG7

Hian7-tai7 lan2 lai5 khoaN3 phiau-gu2 leng7-goa7 chit8-ku3, chiu7-si7 몮Chi3-siong7몯. Chit ku3 oe7 몮Kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im.몯

Tui3 se3-kai3 e5 thoan5-to7 na7-si7 lan2 choe3 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok, soan-kau3 hoe7-gi7 teh khui-hoe7 e5 si5, lan2 eng-kai tioh8 pang3-sak it-chhe3, khi3 chham-ka mui2 chit8 e5 hoe7-gi7. Na7 bo5, lan2 chiu7-si7 bo5 liah8 chit e5 choe3 te7-it, goa2 siong-sin3 chit e5 su7 si7 pi2 it-chhe3 koh khah iau3-kin2 e5, tioh8 eng7 lan2 e5 heng5-tong7 lai5 piau2-si7, lan2 si7 chiong thoan5-to7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5.

Te7 2 tiam2, siat-su2 lan2 na7 chiong se3-kai3 e5 thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, an2-ni lan2 tioh8 chip8-tiong lan2 e5 cheng-sin5, hong7-hian3 ti7 kok-goa7 e5 thoan5-to7, hou7 ki5-thaN bo5 u7 iN7-siong7 e5 lang5 khi3 koan-sim ki5-thaN e5 tai7-chi3. Hiah e5 liah8 kok-lai7 e5 kang-chok thang choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 lang5, si5-siong5 u7 chin-choe7 kang-chok thang choe3. Chong2-si7 tui3 kou2-cha2 kau3 taN chin chio2 lang5 koan-sim ti7 kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok.

Siat-su2 lan2 na7 liah8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, lan2 eng-kai tioh8 pi2 ki5-thaN e5 su7 koh khah toa7 kong3-hian3 ti7 kok-goa7 e5 thoan5-to7 chiah tioh8. ChhiaN2 mng7, li2 na7-si7 seng-li2 lang5 u7 khah choe7 chiN5, li2 beh tau5-chu ti7 ta2-loh8? Tong-jian5 si7 beh tau5-chu ti7 te7-it iau3-kin2 e5 seng-li2. In-ui7 li2 ng3-bang7 beh hoat-tian2 li2 e5 seng-li2 te7-it iau3-kin2 e5 pou7-hun7. Tui3 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7 eng-kai ia7 tioh8 an2-ni. Tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 si7 kau3-hoe7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok, lan2 eng-kai tioh8 chiong lan2 e5 chiN5, tau5-chu ti7 chit e5 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 pou7-hun7. Na7 bo5, lan2 chiu7 m7-si7 chiong goa7-kok thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, in-ui7 lan2 bo5 sin3 che si7 kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok. Goa2 kam2-kak chin chio2 bok8-su, chin chiaN3 teh sin3 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 si7 in choe3 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok.

Chit hang7 su7 goa2 ai3 kong2: 몮Mui2 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7, eng7 ti7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 hui3-iong7 tioh8 pi2 eng7 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 koh khah choe7 chiah tioh8. Che si7 chin u7 hap8-li2 e5, lan2 na7 siong-sin3, tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, an2-ni lan2 eng-kai tioh8 tau5-chu ti7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7, pi2 eng7 ti7 lan2 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 hui3-iong7 koh khah che7.

Ku7-ni5 chiaN-geh8 tui3 goa2 kau3-hoe7 cha-siau3 e5 lang5, goa2 mng7 2 e5 bun7-te5: te7-it, 몮Ku7-ni5 lan2 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 u7 eng7 joa7-choe7 chiN5?몯 In tiau-cha siau3-phou7 ka7 goa2 in3 kong2, 몮Su2-bit8-su phok-su7, li2 ku7-ni5 u7 su2-iong7 4 ban7 5 chheng-khou ti7 li2 pun2 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang-chok몯. Jian5-au7, goa2 chiu7 mng7 te7-ji7 e5 bun7-te5 kong2, 몮Lan2 u7 eng7 joa7-choe7 ti7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7?몯 몮Ku7-ni5 li2 u7 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng-khou ti7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7몯. Goa2 kong2, 몮Chin ho2몯, tan3-si7 lin2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3 m7 tioh8? Si7 lan2 ka-ki7 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng-khou, ia7 tui3 goa7-kok chiah eng7 4 ban7 5 chheng-khou nih? In kong2, 몮M7 si7, goan2 bo5 m7-tioh8, li2 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng-khou ti7 goa7-kok, eng7 4 ban7 5 chheng khou ti7 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7몯. Goa2 in3 kong2, 몮Chin ho2 lah, an2-ni chiah eng-kai, tioh8 siong5-siong5 an2-ni chiah ho2몯. Siat-su2 Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 tiong2-chip na7 lai5 tui3 goa2 kong2, 몮Eng7 ti7 pun2 kau3-hoe7 e5 hui3-iong7, eng-kai tioh8 pi2 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 koh khah choe7몯. An2-ni in tek-khak oe7 liam5-piN chiap-tioh8 goa2 e5 si5-chit-su, chi2-u7 oe7-hiau2 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 eng7 choe7-choe7 chiN5, ia7 m7 goan7-i7 tui3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 eng7 khah choe7 chiN5 e5 kau3-hoe7, goa2 bo5 ai3 choe3 in e5 bok8-su. Goa2 chin hoaN-hi2 goan2 chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 eng7 4 ban7 5 chheng khou, ia7 ti7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng khou.

Sou3-ni5 cheng5 goa2 khai-si2 chhong3-siat Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 si5, goa2 u7 thiaN-tioh8 choe7-choe7 hang7 su7, tan3-si7 u7 chit8-hang7 lang5 bo5 ka7 goa2 kong2. Kau3 ti7 le2-pai3-jit8, goa2 beh khai-si2 thau5 chit8-pai2 kang2-to7 e5 si5, koe3-ke3 bin7 iu-chhiu5 lai5 tui3 goa2 kong2, 몮Su2-bit8-su phok-su7, tu5-liau2 chit8-hang7 i2-goa7, goan2 i2-keng chiong kau3-hoe7 it-chhe3 e5 su7 long2 ka7 li2 kong2 lah.몯 Goa2 theng3-hau7 i tau3-ti2 beh kong2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3. Theng5 chit8-si5-a2 i chiu7 kong2: 몮Chit keng kau3-hoe7 u7 hu7-che3, goan2 u7 chit8-koa2 eng-kai tioh8 lap8 e5 chiN5, be7-tang3 lap8, ti7 koe3-ke3 e5 chhiu2 long2 bo5 chiN5몯. I kong2 liau2-au7 it-tit8 khoaN3 goa2, chhin-chhiuN7 teh ng3-bang7 goa2 oe7 tui3 lak-te7-a2 theh8 chiN5, tui3 i kong2, 몮theh8 chiah e5 chiN5 khi3 heng5 che3.몯

Na7-si7 goa2 bo5 an2-ni choe3, hoan2-tng2 oat8-tng2-sin, kiaN5 khi3 kang2-tai5. Chong2-si7 goa2 teh kiaN5 e5 si5, ki5-to2 kong2, 몮Chu2 ah, goa2 beh tui3 chit8 e5 su7 lai5 chai-iaN2 Seng3-keng lai7-bin7 e5 i3-gi7.몯 Goa2 siuN7 kau3 Seng3-keng kong2, 몮Lin2 tioh8 tai7-seng kiu5 I e5 kok (ui7-tioh8 beh khok-tiong Siong7-te3 e5 kok kau3 choan5 se3-kai3), kap I e5 gi7, chiu7 chiah e5 mih8 long2 beh soa3 hou7 lin2몯. Hit jit8 goa2 ui7-tioh8 kok-goa7 e5 thoan5-to7 lai5 kang2-to7.

Le2-pai3-jit8 am3 lah, si7 goa2 ti7 hia kang2-to7 e5 thau5 chit8 e5 le2-pai3-jit8, goa2 eng-kai tioh8 thoan5 Hok-im e5 to7-li2, chong2-si7 goa2 kam2-kak tioh8 kong2 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 kong2 chit toe5-bak8. Hit me5 goa2 chhiaN2 hoe7-chiong3 ti7 chit le2-pai3 tiong tak8-me5 long2 lai5, in ko2-jian5 long2-chong2 lai5 le2-pai3, in koh-chai3 tui3 goa2 thiaN-tioh8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2. Pai3-ji7 in iah8 tui3 goa2 thiaN-tioh8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, pai3-saN in koh-chai3 thiaN-tioh8 leng7-goa7 chit8 phiN koan-he7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, pai3-si3 am3 goa2 iu5-koh kong2 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2. Pai3-gou7 thiaN-chiong3 cheng-ka, kiam2-chhai2 si7 ui7-tioh8 hi-ki5 e5 in-toaN lai5 e5, chong2-si7 in sou2 thiaN-tioh8 e5 iu5-goan5 si7 chit8-phiN koan-he7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2.

Goa2 teh siuN7 in tek-khak saN-kap teh kong2, 몮Goan2 chit-ui7 sin bok8-su, goan2 chin boe7 liau2-kai2 i, chhin-chhiuN7 tu5-khi3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 i2-goa7 bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 to7-li2 e5 khoan2. TaN te7 2 le2-pai3-jit8 teh beh kau3 lah, kiam2-chhai2 i beh chin chiaN3 khai-si2 kang2-to7.몯

Te7 2 le2-pai3-jit8 kau3 lah, goa2 oe7-ki3-tit hit jit8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 cha7-jit8 chit8-poaN-iuN7, ti7 cha2-khi2-si5 e5 le2-pai3, goa2 po3-ko3 kong2: 몮Kin-a2-jit8 lan2 beh ku2-heng5 3 pai2 e5 le2-pai3, ia7 beh ui7-tioh8 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7 hong7-hian3 3 pai3, thau5 chit8-pai3 si7 cha2-khi2, te7 2 pai3 si7 e7-pou, te7 3 pai2 si7 e7-am3몯. U7 chit8-pou7-hun7 e5 lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 tioh8-kiaN e5 khoan2 teh khoaN3 goa2, na7-si7 goa2 chiu7 khai-si2 goa2 e5 kang-chok lah. Goa2 tit-tioh8 chit8 e5 soan-kau3-su e5 pang-chan7 ke3-oe7 beh khui soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7. Koat-teng7 an2-ni choe3, hit cha2-khi2 goa2 kong2 koan-he7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, ia7 chhiaN2 hoe7-chiong3 tioh8 ui7-tioh8 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7 lai5 hong7-hian3. Ha7-ngou2 am3-si5 e5 chu7-hoe7 long2 saN-tang5, goa2 ti7 chia long2 bo5 kong2 kau3 u7 ui7-tioh8 pun2 kau3-hoe7 lai5 hong7-hian3. Goa2 ia7 chiong sou2 hong7-hian3 e5 cho3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 lou7-eng7. Na7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni koh ke3-siok8 loh8-khi3, oe7 chaiN2-iuN7.

In piN3-choe3 chin koan-sim kok-goa7 thoan5-to7, chham-ka chu7-hoe7 e5 lang5-giah8 jit8-jit8 ke-thiN. Choe7-choe7 leng5-hun5 tit-kiu3, kau3-hoe7 lai7-bin7 e5 che7-ui7 chin kin2 chiu7 che7 moa2, bo5 ku2 in ia7 tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7, sou2-i2 in chiu7 khai-si2 hong7-hian3, hong7-hian3 in koe3-khi3 sou2 m7-bat hong7-hian3 e5. Ti7 kui2 le2-pai3 tiong, chin kin2 chiu7 chiong kau3-hoe7 e5 che3-bu7 long2 heng5 chheng-chhou2, koh tui3 hit jit8 kau3 kin-a2-jit8, ti7 goan2 e5 kang-chok tiong, long2 m7 bat koh khoaN3-kiN3 hu7-che3 chit e5 ji7, goan2 chai-iaN2 goan2 chiong eng-kai he7 ti7 te7-it e5 he7 ti7 te7-it e5 si5, Siong7-te3 pun2-sin chiu7 ka-ki7 kang-chok.

It-poaN e5 kau3-hoe7 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 khun3-lan5, chiu7-si7 chiong chhia he7 ti7 be2 e5 thau5-cheng5, jian5-au7 bok8-su siu7 beng7 khui-chhia, che7 ti7 i e5 ui7 sai2-chhia. Chong2-si7 lan2 na7 chiap-lap8 Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-oe7, lan2 chiu7 chin iong5-iN7 khoaN3 beh khi3 ta2-loh8 chiu7 khi3 ta2-loh8, chhia chiu7 chin ho2 sai2 lah. Sou2-i2 tai7-seng tioh8 lou2-lek8 chiong Siong7-te3 kok khong2-khoah kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, jian5-au7 Siong7-te3 chiu7 oe7 chiong it-chhe3 e5 khiam3-kheh siuN2-su3 lan2, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-oe7 tek-khak boe7 oe7 sit-pai7.

Siat-su2 goa2 na7 siu7 pheng3-chhiaN2 kau3 ti7 leng7-goa7 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7, ia7 hit keng kau3-hoe7 iu5-goan5 u7 hu7-che3, goa2 tek-khak oe7 chiau3 i2-cheng5 e5 choe3-hoat khi3 choe3. Goa2 tek-khak beh khui chit8 e5 toa7 e5 soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, au7-lai5 kiu5 Siong7-te3 lai5 koan-sim toe7-hng e5 che3-bu7. Siong7-te3 tek-khak boe7 kou-hu7 goa2. Sou2-i2 lan2 eng-kai tioh8 choe3 e5, chiu7-si7 tioh8 tai7-seng khi3 choe3, jian5-au7 se3-ji7 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang-chok.

KAU3-HOE7

Te7 3 ku3 goa2 sou2 beh kiong5-tiau e5 chiu7-si7 몮Kau3-hoe7몯 chit ku3 oe7. 몮Kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im몯, goa2 sou2 teh kong2 e5 kau3-hoe7 chiu7-si7 choan5-pou7 e5 kau3-hoe7. Phi3-ju7 lai5 kong2, ti7 Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 bo5 Lu2-soan-to7-hoe7. Goan2 koat-teng7 bo5 ai3 chit khoan2 e5 chou-chit, goa2 m7-si7 hoan2-tui3 chit khoan2 e5 thoan5-the2, goa2 beh ui7-tioh8 mui2 chit8 e5 lu2-soan e5 thoan5-the2 chin kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3. U7 si5 soan-kau3 e5 kng si7 tui3 lu2-soan thoan5-the2 hoat-chhut. Chong2-si7 goa2 ai3 eng7 2 hun-cheng ku2 e5 si5-kan chiu7 beh hou7 li2 beng5-pek8, chit8-khoan2 e5 chou-chit tui3 goan2 si7 bo5 pit-iau3 e5.

Ka2-su2 goa2 ti7 lu2-soan e5 chu7-hoe7, tui3 in kong2, 몮Hian7-chai7 lin2 beh chiaN5 chit8 e5 lu2-soan-kau3-su-thoan5, lin2 sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, che si7 lin2 tak8 e5 sou2 tioh8 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok몯. Na7 an2-ni, i2-au7 goa2 beh tui3 mui2 chit8 lang5, a2-si7 kau3-hoe7 lai7 ki5-thaN chou2-chit kong2-oe7 e5 si5 m7 chai beh an2-choaN2 kong2? Hit si5 goa2 kiam2-chhai2 tioh8 kong2 an2-ni 몮Chit e5 m7 si7 kau3-hoe7 lai7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok, put-ko3 si7 chit8 sio2 pou7-hun7 e5 su7, si7 kau3-hoe7 kang-chok chin choe7 tiong e5 chit8 pou7-hun7 na7-tiaN7, hou7 hiah e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khi3 koan-sim chiu7 ho2, in oe7 koan-sim ti7 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7, sou2 chhun e5 lan2, ---- chiu7-si7 lan2 chiah e5 ta-pou-lang5 ---- lan2 tioh8 choe3 chin-sit8 u7 ke3-tat8 lan2 ta-pou7-lang5 sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5 su7.몯

Bo5! Mui2 chit8 lang5 ti7 goa2 e5 kau3-hoe7, long2 si7 soan-kau3-su hoe7 e5 chit8 hun7-chu2. Goa2 chin ki5-thai7, 80 mia5 a2-si7 koh khah choe7 e5 seng3-koa-tui7-oan5, choan5-pou7 long2 u7 chiap-lap8 in e5 chek-jim7, sou2 u7 e5 tiuN2-lo2, chip-su7, hoe7-iu2, mui2 chit8 e5 chiau-thai7-oan5, mui2 chit8 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5, a2-si7 su7-bu7-oan5, mui2 chit8 e5 ta-pou7 gin2-na2 kap cha-bou2 gin2-na2 long2 tioh8 kong3-hian3 ti7 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7. Goa2 bo5 ai3 pe7-bu2 hong7-hian3 in kiaN2-ji5, goan2 ai3 ka3-si7 gin2-na2 tioh8 hong7-hian3 in ka-ki7, tui3 in 5 hoe3 a2-si7 6 hoe3 e5 si5 in tit-tioh8 chit e5 ka3-si7, kau3 ti7 tiong2-toa7 e5 si5, m7-bian2 koh tui3 pat8-lang5 lai5 hak8-sip8 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 hong7-hian3, a2-si7 pang-chan7 lang5.

Chit e5 kang-chok si7 pi2 sim2-mih8 chou2-chit koh khah iau3-kin2, in-ui7 che si7 siok8 ti7 choan5-pou7 kau3-hoe7. Mui2 chit8 lang5 long2 tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7 e5 si5, chiu7 long2 oe7 khai-si2 kang-chok. Lan2 e5 phiau-gu2 si7, 몮mui2 chit8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 long2 si7 soan-kau3-su몯. Che chiu7-si7 choan5 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang-chok.

SI7 CHAINN2-IUNN7 CHOE3-CHIANN5 E5?

Bo5-lun7 goa2 khi3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, lang5 long2 mng7 goa2 chit e5 bun7-te5. 몮Li2 si7 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 tit-tioh8 chit khoan2 e5 hong7-hian3? Hiah e5 chiN5 si7 tui3 ta2-loh8 lai5 e5? Li2 e5 kau3-hoe7 u7 chin choe7 pah-ban7 pu3-ong mah?몯 Ka-na2-tai7 Thian-chu2-kau3 sin-bun5 e5 phian-chip, khoaN3-tioh8 goan2 e5 po3-ko3-pio2 sou2 kam2-kak e5, i sia2-phoe ka7 goa2 mng7 kong2, 몮Li2 e5 kau3-hoe7 u7 chin choe7 pah-ban7 pu3-ong mah?몯 Goa2 ka7 i in3-kong2: 몮Bo5몯 i chin tioh8-kiaN, au7-lai5 i ti7 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 khan-but8 tiong u7 sia2 chit8-phiN chin tng5 e5 bun5-chiuN kong2, 몮Chit8-ui7 jiat8-sim e5 bok8-su leng2-to7 e5 hong7-hian3 si7 pi2 tui3 An-tai7-liok8 kau3-khu sou2 u7 e5 Thian-chu2-kau3 kau3-hoe7 e5 hong7-hian3 koh khah choe7.몯 I kong2, 몮Lan2 si7 sin3-giong2 e5 chin-sit8 e5 koan2-li2-jin5, chong2-si7 lan2 hou7 chit e5 sin-kau3 e5 kau3-hoe7 iaN5-koe3 lan2, che si7 chit8 kiaN7 chin kian3-siau3 e5 su7몯. Tong-jian5 i e5 i3-su3 si7 beh kek-le7 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin3-tou5 tui3 hong7-hian3 koh khah jiat8-sim. Bo5, goan2 bo5 pah-ban7 e5 pu3-ong, kong2 sit8-chai7 oe7, ti7 goan2 kau3-hoe7, bo5 u7 chit8 e5 u7 chai5-san2 e5 lang5, goan2 e5 hong7-hian3 si7 tui3 chin choe7 peng5-siong5 e5 hoe7-iu2 lai5 e5.

U7 chit8-pai2 chit8 e5 toa7 kau3-phai3 e5 goa7-kok soan-to7-kau3-su7 mng7 goa2 kong2, 몮Kiam2 u7 sim2-mih8 pi3-koat몯. I ai3 chai, siaN2-su7 in kau3-phai3 e5 hong7-hian3 teh kiam2 chio2. Goa2 ka7 i kong2, 몮Bou2-bou2 phok-su7 ah, li2 chiu7-si7 chiong li2 e5 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 hi-seng ti7 u7-sng3 e5 lai7-bin7, li2 kio3 hoe7-iu2 ui7-tioh8 u7-sng3 lai5 hong7-hian3. Jian5-au7 li2 chiong sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 chiN5 chiau3 li2 sou2 khoaN3 choe3 su-iau3 e5 lai5 hun-phoe3. An2-ni choe3 si7 boe7 eng7-tit, li2 boe7 eng7-tit chiong hiah-nih8 iau3-kin2 e5 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7, he7 ti7 u7-sng3 tiong thiu chhut-lai5, he7 ti7 mui2 chit8 e5 lang5 long2 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8 e5 kang2-tai5 teng2. Chin choe7 lam5-lu2 chheng-lian5 siu7 kam2-tong7 beh chi3-goan7 choe3 soan-kau3-su e5 si5, hoe7-chiong3 sou2 su-iau3 e5, peng7 m7 si7 u7-sng3-pio2, chiu7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kam2-tong7몯, i thiaN goa2 kong2 chiah e5 oe7 liau2-au7, chiu7 chan3-seng5 goa2 sou2 kong2 e5.

Goan2 tui3 ta2-loh8 lai5 tit-tioh8 chiah e5? Kiam2-chhai2 goa2 na7 tui3 li2 kong2, it-teng7 oe7 hou7 li2 u7 pang-chan7 chiah tioh8.

Goan2 tit-tioh8 chiah e5 chiN5, m7 si7 tui3 seng3-chhan, chu5-sian7-chhi7 gi7-hoe7, im-gak8-hoe7, chap8-hoe3 be2-be7 lai5 tit-tioh8 e5. Goa2 m7 si7 hoan2-tui3 chiah e5 lai5 tit-tioh8 chiN5, in-ui7 hoe7-iu2bo5 ai3 cho3 chiah e5 tai7-chi3. Chit8 e5 seng-li2 lang5 teh choe3 i sou2 bo5 ai3 e5 seng-li2, i kiam2 oe7 seng5-kong? Hian7-chai7 goan2 teh chi-chhi5 350 mia5 e5 soan-kau3-su, mui2 ko3-geh8 goan2 tioh8 ai3 u7 2 ban7 khou, na7 bo5, hiah e5 soan-kau3-su oe7 tu2-tioh8 kan-khou2. ChhiaN2 mng7, lin2 cho3 seng-li2 e5 lang5 u7 kui2 e5 u7 chiah nih8 toa7 e5 chek-jim7 neh? Siat-su2 li2 mui2 ko3-geh8 na7 it-teng7 tioh8 ai3 u7 2 ban7-khou, li2 beh an2-choaN2? Siat-su2 na7 u7 350 mia5 e5 kang-lang5, teh oa2-kho3 li2 lai5 seng-oah8 e5 si5 li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7? Goa2 ai3 ka7 li2 kong2: 몮Siong7-te3 tek-khak bo5 kou-hu7 lang5, bo5-lun7 goa2 ti7 kok-lai7 a2-si7 kok-goa7, ti7 Eng-kok, O3-tai7-li7-a khui po3-to7-tai7-hoe7 sou2 su-iau3 e5 kim-chiN5 long2 bo5 khiam3-kheh, chiau3 siong5 tit-tioh8 ia7 chiau3 siong5 chi-chhut몯.

Hian7-chai7 chhiaN2 ka7 goa2 kong2, 몮Li2 kiam2 bat tui3 chap8-hoe3 e5 be2-be7 tit-tioh8 2 ban7 khou? Na7-si7 bo5, choe3 hit e5 su7 u7 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7? An2-ni goa2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3? Tong-jian5 tioh8 oaN7 pat8-khoan2 e5 hong-hoat, chiu7-si7 oe7-thang tit-tioh8 kau3-giah8 e5 kim-chiN5 e5 hong-hoat. Choe7-choe7 lang5 u7 chit-khoan2 e5 siuN7-hoat chiu7-si7, 몮Kiau-ti7 Bou7-lek8 si2-khi3 e5 si5, Kiau-ti7 Bou7-lek8 e5 Siong7-te3 ia7 si2-khi3.몯 Chong2-si7 goa2 ai3 kong2 Siong7-te3 boe7 oe7 si2, I2-li7-a e5 Siong7-te3 hian7-chai7 iau2 teh oah8, I oe7 choe3-chhut sou2 su-iau3 e5 sin5-jiah. 몮Goa2 ka7 li2 kong2, li2 na7 sin3 goa2, li2 kiam2 boe7 khoaN3-kiN3 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng? Sin3 e5 lang5 hoan7-su7 long2 oe7.몯

Koe3-khi3 30 ni5 ku2 mui2 ni5 goan2 long2 khui soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, ki5-kan si7 4 le2-pai3 ku2, u7 5 e5 le2-pai3-jit8. Chu7-hoe7 chit8 jit8 3 pai2, cha2-khi2-si5, e7-tau3-si5, e7-am3-si5, tai7-seng hou7 chham-ka chu7-hoe7 e5 lang5 u7 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7 e5 iN7-siong7 liau2-au7, goan2 chiu7 ku2-heng5 kho3 sin3-sim e5 hong7-hian3, goan2 e5 hoe7-chiong3 chiu7 piau2-si7 ti7 beh lai5 e5 12 ko3-geh8 tiong sou2 pe7-thang hong7-hian3 e5 sou3-bok8.

Pho-su-tun3 Kong-hng5-lou7 kau3-hoe7, u7 chit8 pai2 chhiaN2 goa2 khi3 khui pou3-to7 tai7-hoe7, goa2 chiu7 khi3. Hit si5 hoe7-tiuN5 lang5 che7 kau3 moa2-moa2, chin choe7 lang5 bo5 che7-ui7. Khia7 e5 toa7-pou7-hun7, long2 si7 chheng-lian5 lang5, long2 u7 chiap-lap8 Ki-tok. Kau3-hoe7 e5 bok8-su chhiaN2 goa2 kau3 i e5 pan7-kong-sek, ka7 goa2 kong2 몮Su2-bit8-su7 phok-su7, chit keng kau3-hoe7 135 ni5 e5 lek8-su2 tiong m7-bat khui chit8 pai2 e5 soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7. Goan2 chai li2 ti7 li2 e5 kau3-hoe7 mui2 ni5 long2 u7 khui chit8 pai2, li2 u7 hoaN-hi2 ui7-tioh8 goan2 khui chit8 pai2 hit-khoan2 e5 hoe7 mah? Goa2 mng7 i e5 kau3-hoe7 tng-si5 chit8 ni5 tiong hian3 joa7 che7 ti7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7. I in3-tap si7 chit8 ni5 3 chheng 2 pah khou. Sou2-i2 keh ni5 goa2 chiu7 toa3 chit8 kun5 e5 soan-kau3-su kau3 i e5 kau3-hoe7 khi3 khui soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, i2-au7 6 ni5 ku2 goa2 ke3-siok8 ti7 hia khui chit khoan2 e5 hoe7-gi7. Ku7-ni5 hit keng kau3-hoe7 u7 hong7-hian3 27 ban7 6 chheng khou choe3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 lou7-iong7. Kam2-sia7 Chu2, ti7 koe3-khi3 kui2-ni5 ku2 u7 tui3 3 chheng 2 pah khou chin3-pou7 kau3 27 ban7 6 chheng khou, che long2 si7 soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7 e5 kiat-ko2.

Koh chit8 e5 le7 chiu7-si7 goa2 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7, 30 ni5 cheng5 goa2 u7 khui chit8 pai2 soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, hit ni5 e5 hong7-hian3 si7 3 chheng 5 pah khou, na7-si7 kin-ni5 choe3-au7 chit8 pian3, goan2 sou2 siu e5 hong7-hian3 si7 31 ban7 4 chheng khou. Hian7-chai7 goan2 sou2 u7 e5 kim-giah8 si7 chhiau-koe3 450 ban7 khou, che si7 soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7 sou2 choe3 e5. Che si7 beh hou7 hoe7-chiong3 tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7 e5 hoat-tou7, in tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7 e5 si5-chun7, chiu7 khai-si2 hong7-hian3 lah.

Che m7 si7 chin khun3-lan5 e5 su7, mui2 chit8 keng e5 kau3-hoe7 long2 thang choe3. Li2 tioh8 khoaN3 tak8 lang5 u7 tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7, long2 u7 hun7 ti7 chit e5 iN7-siong7 e5 kang-chok. Kui2-ni5 cheng5 goan2 tak8-lang5 e5 hian3-kim peng5-kin si7 1 ni5 5 khou, chong2-si7 u7 3000 mia5 e5 hong7-hian3 chia2, sou2-i2 goan2 chiu7 tit-tioh8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 hong7-hian3 1 ban7 5 chheng khou. Choe3 kin7 in chit8 ni5 peng5-kin e5 hong7-hian3 si7 10 khou, an2-ni goan2 chit8 ni5 chiu7 oe7-thang tit-tioh8 3 ban7 khou e5 hong7-hian3. Au7-lai5 in chin3-pou7 kau3 15 khou, goan2 chiu7 tit-tioh8 4 ban7 5 chheng khou. Chit khoan2 e5 hong7-hian3 boe7 thang sng3 choe3 sim2-mih8, chi2-u7 oe7 thang kong2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 gin2-na2 teh thit-tho5 e5 hong7-hian3, in-ui7 toa7-pou7-hun7 e5 ta-pou gin2-na2 chit8 ni5 chi3-chio2 ia7 oe7 than3 15 khou, na7 an2-ni chit ko3-geh8 chi2-u7 si7 chit8 khou-gin5 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 e5 soe3-kiaN2 Po2-lo5, ti7 sou3-ni5 cheng5, u7 choe3 tam7-poh8 e5 mih8-kiaN7 chhut khi3 boe7, chiong sou2 tit e5 long2 hong7-hian3. Goa2 e5 ka-teng5 sou2 hian3 e5 si7 Po2-lo5 sou2 hian3 e5 2 poe7, long2-chong2 sng3, goan2 hit ni5 peng5-kin mui2 lang5 u7 96 khou e5 hong7-hian3. Lin2 sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5, chiu7-si7 tioh8 hou7 mui2 chit8 e5 hoe7-chiong3 u7 iN7-siong7, mui2 chit8 e5 hoe7-chiong3 long2 chiaN5-choe3 u7 kui-ku2 e5 hong7-hian3 chia2, an2-ni bun7-toe5 chiu7 kai2-koat lah.

U7 chit8 e5 kou3-su7 kong2, Ia5-sou to3-tng2 khi3 thiN-teng2, I ti7 hia tu2-tioh8 thiN-sai3 Ka-pek-liat8. Chu2 kong2, I ti7 toe7-bin7 chiuN7 i2-keng oan5-seng5 kang-chok.

Ka-pek-liat8 mng7 kong2: 몮An2-ni li2 e5 ke3-oe7 si7 siaN2-khoan2, chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 hou7 hok-im thoan5 khui-khoah? Li2 u7 lau5 chit8 e5 toa7 e5 chou2-chit kap ho2 e5 ke3-oe7?몯

Kiu3-chu2 in3 kong2, 몮Bo5, goa2 bo5 lau5 sim2-mih8 khoan2 e5 chou2-chit; chi2-u7 chit8 sio2-khoa2 e5 hak8-seng, in e5 chhut-sin long2 si7 san3-chhiah, in oe7 chiong hok-im thoan5 chhut-khi3.몯

Ka-pek-liat8 kong2: 몮Siat-su2 in na7 bo5 an2-ni choe3, Li2 kiam2 u7 sim2-mih8 ke3-oe7?몯

Kiu3-chu2 pi-siong in3 kong2: 몮Goa2 bo5 ki5-thaN e5 ke3-oe7.몯

Chiong-lai5 u7 chit8-jit8, chhian-chhian ban7-ban7 e5 iN7-pang lang5 beh ti7 Chu2 e5 po2-cho7 cheng5, eng7 chhiu2 chi2 lan2, chek-pi7 lan2, in beh khau3 chhut-lai5 kong2: 몮Bo5 chit8 e5 lang5 koan-sim goa2 e5 leng5-hun5.몯 Li2 kap goa2 beh chhut toa7-siaN, siuN7 beh lai5 pian7-kai2 kong2, 몮Chu2, goa2 kiam2 si7 teh kou3-siu2 goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7 mah?몯 Chu2 beh in3 li2 kong2: 몮Li2 hiaN-ti7 e5 huih u7 siaN2 tui3 A-hui-li7-ka, A-se-a, cheng3 hai2-to2 ng3 goa2 ai-kio3.몯 Li2 hiaN-ti7 e5 huih e5 siaN, si7, li2 beh tit-kiu3 kau3 thian-tong5, chong2-si7 li2 hiaN-ti7 e5 huih ti7 li2 e5 chhiu2-nih, chiu7-si7 hiah e5 kap li2 chiap-chhiok e5 lang5 e5 huih.

Beh choe3 siu2-bang7 e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 m7-si7 chit8 kiaN7 khin-sang e5 su7. 몮Goa2 beh ti7 li2 e5 chhiu2-tiong tho2 i e5 huih.몯 Kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok, chiu7-si7 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7, tui3 chit-kiaN7 su7, chhiN2 mng7, li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 choe3?

 
TE7 4 CHIUNN
SIONG7-TE3 CHAINN2-IUNN7 KIO3 GOA2 CHOE3 SE3-KAI3 THOAN5-TO7 E5 KANG

ChhiaN2 hian-khui Ma2-thai3 hok-im 9 chiuN 35-38 chat 몮Ia5-sou pian3 kiaN5 chiah e5 siaN5 chiah e5 hiuN-sia7...몯 chhiaN2 chu3-i3 I kau3 tak8 e5 siaN5, tak8 e5 hiuN-sia7, I bo5 tiam3 ti7 chit8 e5 thoan5-the2, Ia5-sou bo5 cho3 bok8-su, I si5-siong5 teh kiaN5. 몮Ia5-sou pian3 kiaN5 chiah e5 siaN5 chiah e5 hiuN-sia7...... thoan5 thian-kok e5 hok-im몯.

몮I khoaN3-kiN3 hiah e5 cheng3-lang5 chiu7 kho2-lin5 in몯. Sim2-mih8 si7 kho2-lin5? Kho2-lin5 m7-si7 tong5-cheng5, kho2-lin5 chiu7-si7 thiN3 e5 tong7-chok, lan2 u7 kho2-lin5 e5 sim a2-bo5? Na7 u7, tioh8 choe3 Chu2 sou2 choe3 e5.

몮Chiu7 ka7 I e5 hak8-seng kong2, thang siu-seng5 e5 si7 choe7, choe3 kang e5 si7 chio2몯. Che si7 tng-si5 e5 bun7-toe5, siang7-khoan2 I e5 si5-tai7 e5 bun7-toe5 ia7-si7 lan2 kin-a2-jit8 e5 bun7-toe5. Thang siu-seng5 e5 si5 choe7, choe3 kang e5 si5 chio2, na7-si7 an2-ni beh chaiN2-iuN7 kai2-koat chit e5 bun7-toe5? Seng3-keng kong2, 몮Sou2-i2 lin2 tioh8 kiu5 hng5-chu2 pek kang khi3 ka7 I siu-seng5.몯

GOA2 KIAM2 THANG TIANN7-TIANN7 TOA3 KA-NA2-TAI7?

Kui2-ni5 cheng5 goa2 chiong Seng3-keng thak8 chin sek8, bok8-tek si7 ai3 khoaN3 goa2 tau3-ti2 thang tiaN7-tiaN7 ti7 Ka-na2-tai7, koh u7 hok8-chiong5 Siong7-te3. Goa2 mng7 ka-ki7, goa2 si7 ai3 tiam3 ti7 Ka-na2-tai7 choe3 khin-sang e5 bok8-hoe7 kang-chok, an2-ni choe3, Siong7-te3 oe7 moa2-chiok a2-boe7?

Chong2-si7 goa2 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 si5, goa2 hoat-kian3 tioh8 chit khoan2 e5 piau2-si7: Ban7-kok, ban7-bin5, ban7-chok8, choan5 se3-kai3, tak8-iuN7 e5 gian5-gu2, peh-siN3, kok-ka, toe7-kek8. OaN7 chit8-ku3 oe7 lai5 kong2 goa2 sou2 hoat-kian3 e5 chiu7-si7, hok-im si7 beh siuN2-su3 choan5 se3-kai3, tak8 e5 pang-kok, ban7-chok8, ban7-lui7, tak8-khoan2 e5 khiuN-khau2, tak8-iuN7 e5 peh-siN3 e5, sou2-i2 lang5-lang5 long2 eng-kai tioh8 thiaN.

Goa2 khoaN3 tioh8 chiah e5 Seng3-keng chat, goa2 chiu7 mng7 chit8 e5 bun7-toe5, sou2 u7 e5 kok-ka long2 ti7 Ka-na2-tai7? Na7-si7 goa2 chiu7 thang tiam3 ti7 goa2 e5 kok-ka, ti7 chia thoan5 hok-im, m7 bian2 chhut-khi3 kau3 pat8 ui7; chong2-si7 na7 u7 chit8 e5 kok-ka ti7 Ka-na2-tai7 kok-keng2 i2-goa7, an2-ni goa2 chiu7 u7 gi7-bu7, tioh8 li7-khui goa2 e5 kok-ka, chhut-khi3 kau3 ki5-thaN e5 kok-ka. Goa2 na7 boe7 thang khi3, ia7 tioh8 phai3 lang5 the3 goa2 khi3. Chit 2 hang7 goa2 long2 bo5 khi3 choe3, an2-ni goa2 ti7 po3-siuN2 e5 jit8-chi2 oe7 sit-loh8 sou2 u7 e5 po3-siuN2.

Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, li2 sim2-mih8 khoan2? Li2 i2-keng chai hok-im tioh8 thoan5 kau3 ti7 ban7-pang, ban7-kok, choan5 se3-kai3, ban7-chok8 ban7-lui7, tak8 khoan2 e5 gian5-gu2 tit8 kau3 toe7-kek8. ChhiaN2 mng7 koan-he7 chit e5 su7 li2 u7 choe3 sim2-mih8? Li2 u7 ke3-oe7 beh an2-choaN2 khi3 choe3 mah? Li2 beh ka-ki7 khi3 a2-si7 beh phai3 lang5 khi3. Nng7 hang7 long2 oe7 eng7-tit, chong2-si7 li2 na7 2 hang7 long2 bo5 choe3, li2 si7 u7 chai-e7, Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7 li2 tek-khak tioh8 sun7-hok8, tek-khak tioh8 kiaN Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7, in-ui7 bo5 lou7 thang siam2-pi7 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7.

GOA2 SIUNN7 AI3 CHHUT-KHI3

Goa2 18 hoe3 hit ni5, goa2 bat khi3 Eng-siok8 Kou-lun5-pi2-a In3-te7-an lang5 hia, toa3 ti7 kin7 A-lah-su7-ka e5 In3-te7-an lang5 e5 chhau2-chhu3 nih, li7 goa2 e5 chhu3 u7 4000 li2 e5 sou2-chai7. Tiam3 hia u7 1 ni5 goa7 ku2; au7-lai5 goa2 kam2-kak goa2 tioh8 koh siu7 kau3-iok8, sou2-i2 choe3-au7 chiu7 koh to3-tng2 kau3 bun5-hoa3 toe7-tai3. Thak8 5 ni5 ku2 e5 sin5-hak8, pit8-giap8 liau2-au7 chiu7 siu7 hong-lip8 choe3 thoan5 hok-im e5 kang-chok, liau2-au7 koh chai3 ke3-siok8 chit8 ni5 e5 gian2-kiu3 kang-chok.

Au7-lai5 goa2 tui3 TiuN2-lo2-hoe7 kok-goa7 soan-to7-hoe7 chi3-goan7 beh kau3 In3-tou7 kang-chok. In chin siong5-se3 kho2-lu7 goa2 e5 chi3-goan7, goa2 ia7 ko3-jin5 khi3 soan-to7-hoe7 chhoe7 in, kau3-boe2 bo5 un2-chun2 goa2. Soan-to7-hoe7 khoaN3 goa2 bo5 hah8 ti7 choe3 soan-kau3-su e5 kang-chok. Goa2 to3-tng2 kau3 goa2 e5 kou3-hiong kang-chok, chiu7 choe3 To-lun5-to Tat8-li7 tiuN2-lo2 kau3-hoe7 e5 bok8-su, au7-lai5 choe3 soan-to7-hoe7 e5 bok8-su. Chong2-si7 goa2 bo5 liah8 chit e5 choe3 moa2-chiok, goa2 chai goa2 tek-khak tioh8 siuN7 pan7-hoat; in-ui7 goa2 i2-keng chin chheng-chhou2 khoaN3-kiN3 iN7-siong7. Choe3-au7, goa2 ka-ki7 kau3 Au-chiu e5 Sou-ngou5 soan-kau3-khu tui3 chin khoah e5 khu-hek8, chiu7-si7 Liap8-thoat-ui2-a, Ai3-so-ni5-a, Pho-lan5 teng2 e5 sou2-chai7 kang-chok, kiat-ko2 u7 tit-tioh8 chin-choe8 e5 leng5-hun5 kui Ki-tok. Goa2 thoan5-kau3 goa2 e5 sin-the2 phah phaiN2, chiu7 hun7-khi3 lah. Sou2-i2 goa2 chiah tng2-lai5 goa2 e5 chhu3.

Goa2 u7 lu2-heng5 choan5 Bi2-kok kap Ka-na2-tai7, khui pou3-to7 tai7-hoe7, na7-si7 choe3-au7 goa2 koh kam2-kak tioh8 chhut-kok. Sou2-i2 goa2 chit pai2 chiu7 kau3 Se-pan-ga5, chong2-si7 goa2 iu7 koh phoa3-piN7, put-tek-put koh to3-tng2 lai5 chhu3-nih.

Au7-lai5 goa2 ti7 To-lun5-to chong3-siat Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7, si7 Chu2-au7 1930 ni5 e5 su7. 2 ni5 au7 goa2 koh chit8 pai2 siu7 kam2-tong7 khi3 Hui-chiu. Goa2 tit-tioh8 To-ma2 Lan-pek phok-su7 e5 tang5-phoaN7, 2 lang5 khia5 be2 kau3 Hui-chiu e5 lai7-toe7 khi3, chit8 jit8 kiaN5 30 li2, choe3-au7 koh ti7 Hui-chiu chin toa7 e5 chhau2-na5 tiong to2 loh8-khi3, peN7 kau3 chin li7-hai7. Lak8 le2-pai3 chiah ho2 khi2-lai5, sou2-i2 koh chit8 pai2 to3-tng2 kau3 ti7 bun5-beng5 e5 sou2-chai7.

Chit si5 goa2 chiah khai-si2 kam2-kak tng-si5 soan-to7-hoe7 e5 koat-teng7 si7 tioh8, in-ui7 goa2 bo5 sek-hap8 ti7 soan-kau3-su e5 kang-chok. Chong2-si7 goa2 i2-keng tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7, goa2 chai-iaN2 ki5-thaN kok-ka e5 peh-siN3 chin su-iau3 thiaN hok-im. Sou2-i2 Chu2-au7 1938 ni5 goa2 chiu7 koh chai3 chhut-khi3 goa7-kok pou3-to7, beh chin7 goa2 sou2 eng-kai tioh8 e5 kang-chok lai5 chiaN5 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 e5 bok8-phiau. Chit pai2 goa2 u7 khi3 Thai3-peng5-iuN5, mi5-jit8 che7 chun5 31 jit8 ku2, goa2 kam2-kak tioh8 chiong hok-im thoan5 hou7 hiah e5 chiah8-lang5 e5 bin5-chok8 kap thou2-lang5, kap So2-lo5-bun5 kun5-to2 e5 lang5, hou7 in choe3 Ki-tok-tou5. Chong2-si7 bo5 ku2 goa2 chiu7 hoan7-tioh8 koaN5-jiat8 peN7, i-ti7 3 ni5 chiah ho2 khi2 lai5. Chit tiong-kan chit8 pai2 koh chit8 pai2, chit8 ko3-geh8 koh chit8 ko3-geh8 goa2 e5 phoa3-piN7 long2 boe7 ho2 khi2-lai5, kau3 be2 i-seng kap ki5-thaN soan-kau3-su, chiong goa2 koh-chai3 sang3 tng2-khi3 To-lun5-to kang-chok.

Chong2-si7 goa2 boe7 thang theng5-chi2, goa2 long2-chong2 u7 hong2-bun7 66 e5 kok-ka, hian7-chai7 goa2 iau2 si7 teh siuN7 ai3 khi3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7.

GOA2 SANG3 TAI7-LI2 E5 LANG5 CHHUT-KHI3

Goa2 tu2 chiah khai-si2 bok8-hoe7 e5 si5, goa2 kam2-kak ka-ki7 boe7 thang chhut-khi3, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 siuN7 ai3 phai3 tai7-li2 e5 lang5 chhut-khi3. U7 chit8 jit8 goa2 tu2-tioh8 Lam5-bi2 chiu Pou3-to7 lian5-beng5 e5 Koa Bok8-su. Goa2 ka7 i kong2: 몮Li2 u7 beh phai3 sin e5 soan-kau3-su chhut-khi3 a2-bo5?몯 I in3 goa2 kong2: 몮U7, goan2 i2-keng u7 5 e5 chun2-pi7 beh chhut-khi3.몯 Goa2 koh ka7 i mng7, 몮SiaN2-su7 bo5 beh koaN2-kin2 sang3 in chhut-khi3?몯 I in3 kong2: 몮In-ui7 goan2 bo5 chiN5.몯 Goa2 koh mng7 i kong2: 몮Siat-su2 goa2 na7 oe7 thang ka7 in chun2-pi7 lu2-hui3, li2 beh un2-chun2 goan2 lai5 kiong-kip in?몯 I chin hoaN-hi2 lai5 tah-eng3.

Goa2 u7 chhiaN2 hit 5 e5 soan-kau3-su khia7 ti7 bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang2-tai5 teng2, iau3-kiu5 hoe7-iu2 tioh8 chhe-phai3 in chhut-khi3. In ko2-jian5 an2-ni choe3, i2-au7 siu7 chhe e5 lang5 5 e5 piN3 choe3 10 e5, 10 e5 piN3 choe3 20 e5, 20 e5 piN3 choe3 40 e5, 40 e5 piN3 choe3 100 e5, 100 e5 piN3 choe3 200 e5, 200 e5 piN3 choe3 350 e5.Hian7-chai7 goan2 i2-keng u7 ui7 Chu2 choe3 kang e5 kun-tui7, choe3 goan2 e5 tai7-li2 chia2 kau3 ti7 40 e5 goa7-kok soan-kau3-khu, ti7 35 e5 thoan5-the2 e5 soan-to7-hoe7 e5 e7-bin7 teh kang-chok, goan2 hu7-chek in 몮ko3-jin5-tek e5 seng-oah8.몯

Chong2-si7 goa2 iau2 bo5 moa2-chiok, goa2 siong5-siong5 ki5-to2 kong2: 몮Chu2 ah, siat-su2 na7-si7 Li2 e5 chi2-i3, chhiaN2 Li2 hou7 goa2 oah8 kau3 goan2 oe7-thang chhe-phai3 400 e5 soan-kau3-su kau3 ti7 goa7-kok khi3.몯 Goa2 kam2-kak Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 eng-kai tioh8 phai3 400 e5, na7 bo5 goa2 si7 boe7 moa2-chiok.

Che si7 goa2 oah8 ti7 se3-kan e5 bok8-tek, goa2 choe3 bok8-su si7 te7 2 iau3-kin2 e5 su7, goa2 siuN7 choe3 soan-kau3-su si7 te7-it iau3-kin2, goa2 tu3-chok seng3-si si7 te7 2 iau3-kin2 e5 su7, goa2 siuN7 beh chhut-khi3, sit8-che3 siong7, goa2 ka-ki7 u7 chhut-khi3, chong2-si7 tak8 pai2 long2 put-tek-put tioh8 tng2 lai5. Sou2-i2 goa2 chai-iaN2 eng-kai tioh8 cho3 chit8 hang7 su7; chiu7-si7 sang3 pat8-lang5 chhut-khi3, che ia7 si7 goa2 khi3 choan5 Bi2-kok, Ka-na2-tai7, O3-tai7-li2-a, Niu2-se-lan5, Lam5 Hui-chiu, Eng-kok e5 bok8-tek. Goa2 khi3 khui soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, kou3-le7 chheng-lian5 lang5, tek-khak tioh8 chin7 lan2 sou2 oe7 khi3 chhoe7 koh chhe tai7-li2 chia2 chhut-khi3.

KOH LAI5 E5 HIONG-TIN3

Tu2-chiah goa2 u7 thak8 Seng3-keng hou7 li2 thiaN, Ia5-sou chaiN2-iuN7 pian3-kiaN5 tak8 e5 sou2-chai7, li2 iau2 oe7 ki3-tit boe7? Chu2 Ia5-sou ti7 bou2 chit8 e5 siaN5-tin3 khui pou3-to7-hoe7 liau2-au7, hit mi5 hut-jian5-kan bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lah. Keh cha2-khi2 chin cha2, I e5 hak8-seng chin chiaN3 tioh8-kip koaN2-kin2 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 chhoe7 I, au7-lai5 chhoe7 tioh8 Ia5-sou ti7 soaN-teng2 e5 sou2-chai7 teh ki5-to2.

In chiu7 kio3 kong2: 몮Chu2 ah, cheng3-lang5 long2 teh theng3-hau7 li2, u7 e5 phoa3-piN7 lang5 ai3 Li2 i-ti7, to3-tng2 lai5 khi3 oan5-seng5 Li2 e5 kang-chok, iah8 u7 e5 cha-hng thiaN Li2 to7-li2 e5 lang5, iu5-goan5 ti7 siaN5-tin3 teh theng3-hau7 Li2, ai3 thiaN Li2 e5 oe7.몯

Si7 Goa2 thang siong2-siong7 hit si5 Chu2 chaiN2-iuN7 ka7 in in3-tap, I e5 bak8-chiu hng7-hng7 teh khoaN3 soaN-kok hit peng5, koh khoaN3 hng7-hng7 hit peng5 e5 soaN, jian5-au7 kong2: 몮Goa2 tek-khak tioh8 khi3 pat8 e5 siaN5-chhi7 thoan5-to7, in-ui7 goa2 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni siu7 chhe-khian3 e5몯 I siong5-siong5 teh siuN7 pat8 e5 siaN5-chhi7, keh-piah e5 siaN5-chhi7, koh lai5 e5 siaN5-chhi7, I siong5-siong5 teh siuN7 hiah e5 I iau2 boe7 khi3 thoan5 hok-im e5 hiah e5 siaN5-chhi7; I chin ai3 kau3 hia, hou7 lang5 thiaN-kiN3 hok-im. I siong5-siong5 teh siuN7 kau3 몮ki5-thaN e5 iuN5몯.

Po2-lo5 ia7 u7 siang7 khoan2 e5 iN7-siong7, i ia7 siong5-siong5 kong2, 몮Khah hng7 e5 sou2-chai7몯, iau2 boe7 u7 hok-im thoan5-kau3 e5 sou2-chai7, i kong2 i ai3 khi3 Se-pan-ga5, i ia7 chai hok-im tioh8 thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3.

Li2 kiam2 chai-iaN2 bat u7 chit8 si5 hok-im u7 thoan5 kau3 ti7 choan5 pak-pou7 Hui-chiu e5 sou2-chai7 mah? Hia bat u7 kui2-na7-pah keng e5 kau3-hoe7, li2 kiam2 chai-iaN2 cha2-si5 e5 toa7 sin5-hak8-ka u7 choe7-choe7 si7 tui3 pak-pou7 Hui-chiu chhut-lai5? Chong2-si7 au7-lai5 pak-pou7 Hui-chiu soa3 piN3-chiaN5 choe3 Hoe5-hoe5 kau3 kok. Koe3-khi3 kui2-na7-pah ni5 tiong-kan, Ki-tok-kau3 ti7 hia chin khun3-lan5 thoan5 chhut-khi3. Chhin-chhiuN7 lah8-chek e5 hoe2 ju2 lai5 ju2 sio2, choe3-au7 soa3 hoa khi3, koe3-khi3 u7 chit8 si5 hui-siong5 e5 kng-beng5, na7-si7 hian7-chai7 soa3 hoa khi3. Chit khoan2 e5 tai7-chi3 beh choaN2-iuN7 kai2-sek nih? ChhiaN2 iong5-un2 goa2 ka7 li2 kong2.

Pak-pou7 Hui-chiu e5 leng2-to7-chia2 kap sin5-hak8-ka, ti7 i2-cheng5 bat u7 chit8 e5 si5-ki5, bo5 teh thoan5 hok-im, tai7-ke teh oan-ke, chin li7-hai7. In khai-si2 tui3 sin5-hak8 tho2-lun7, ia7 saN-kap pian7-lun7 koan-he7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 to7-li2. In eng-kai tioh8 khi3 lam5-peng5 pat8 e5 siaN5-chhi7, koh kau3 pat8 e5 siaN5-chhi7 khi3 thoan5-to7 chiah tioh8. Siat-su2 in na7 an2-ni choe3, tek-khak ti7 te2 e5 si5-kan oe7 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 Khai-pho2-tun, au7-lai5 kau3 ti7 choan5-pou7 Hui-chiu. An2-ni Hui-chiu chiu7 chin kho2-leng5 ti7 kui2-na7-pah ni5-cheng5 long2 tit-tioh8 hok-im, kiam2-chhai2 oe7 sang3 soan-kau3-su lai5 Bi2-kok, Au-chiu e5 sou2-chai7.

HiaN-ti7 ah! Chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 su7 chin kho2-leng5 oe7 hoat-seng ti7 lan2 e5 sou2-chai7. Kim-jit8 ti7 Bi2-kok, Ka-na2-tai7, Eng-kok, O3-tai7-li7-a, Niu2-se-lan5 e5 kau3-hoe7 chin che7 long2 piN3-chiaN5 choe3 sia7-hoe7 e5 khu-lok8-pou7. Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 kau3-hoe7 na7 bo5 chhiN2 khi2-lai5, koaN2-kin2 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 ti7 choan5 se3-kai3, an2-ni hoat-seng ti7 Hui-chiu e5 su7 ia7 oe7 hoat-seng ti7 lan2.

SE3-KAI3 SI7 CHOE3-KANG E5 SOU2-CHAI7

Kiam2-chhai2 li2 beh mng7, 몮Chong2-si7, lan2 chia e5 lang5, long2 iau2 boe7 tit-kiu3, siaN2-su7 tioh8 ai3 chhut-khi3 nih? Ti7 lan2 chia iau2 u7 choe7-choe7 e5 kang-chok tioh8 ai3 choe3, iau2 boe7 u7 chhut-khi3 goa7-kok kang-chok i2-cheng5 siaN2-su7 bo5 teh chiong kok-lai7 e5 kang-chok oan5-seng5 nih?몯 Goa2 na7 kau3 ti7 tak8 sou2-chai7, lang5 long2 an2-ni ka7 goa2 mng7. Hian7-chai7 iong5-un2 goa2 eng7 3, 4 e5 bun7-toe5 lai5 in3-tap chit e5 bun7-toe5.

Te7-it ---- siaN2-su7 mui2 chit8 e5 Sou-kek-lan5 lang5 long2-chong2 iau2 boe7 choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 i2-cheng5 Tai7-pit8 Li2-bun5-su-tun (David Livingston) chiu7 khi3 Hui-chiu? Iau2 u7 chin choe7 Sou-kek-lan5 lang5 long2 iau2 boe7 sin3 Ki-tok, chong2-si7 Li2-bun7-su-tun chiu7 li7-khui i ka-ki7 e5 sou2-chai7, kau3 ti7 ou-am3 e5 Hui-chiu, goa2 ai3 mng7 li2 ---- che si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3?

Te7 2, siaN2-su7 mui2 chit8 e5 Eng-kok lang5 long2 iau2 boe7 chiaN5 choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 i2-cheng5 Ui7-liam5 Khia-li2 (William Carey) chiu7 khi3 In3-tou7 nih?

Te7 3, siaN2-su7 mui2 chit8 e5 Bi2-kok lang5 long2 iau2-boe7 chiaN5-choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 i2-cheng5, Ja2-tek-sun (Judson) chiu7 li7-khui Bi2-kok khi3 Bian7-tian7 nih? Si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3? Kiam2 m7-si7 iau2 u7 chin choe7 Bi2-kok lang5 long2 iau2 boe7 chiaN5-choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 mah?

Choe3-au7 chit e5 bun7-toe5, siaN2-su7 Pa-lek-su7-tan3 iau2 boe7 long2-chong2 thiaN-tioh8 hok-im i2-cheng5 su3-tou5 Po2-lo5 chiu7 khi3 Au-chiu nih? Po2-lo5 u7 keng-koe3 siong-tong e5 kho2-lu7 liau2-au7, chiah li7-khui i e5 kok-ka kau3 Au-chiu, beh chiong hok-im thoan5-pian3, siaN2-su7?  I kiam2 m7-si7 eng-kai tioh8 ti7 Pa-lek-su7-tan3, chi3-chio2 tioh8 hou7 hiah e5 lang5 long2 thiaN-kiN3 hok-im?

Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, chia chi2-u7 chit8 e5 in3-tap, chiu7 si7 Seng3-keng e5 chit8 ku3 oe7, 몮se3-kai3 chiu7-si7 choe3 kang e5 sou2-chai7몯, Bi2-kok m7-si7 se3-kai3, Eng-kok ia7 m7 si7 se3-kai3, kang-chok e5 sou2-chai7 si7 choan5 se3-kai3. Li2 m7-bat thiaN-tioh8 chit8 e5 choh-sit lang5 chi2-u7 ti7 i chhan5-hng5 sio2-sio2 e5 chit8 kak teh choe3-kang. Choh-sit lang5 si7 ti7 chhan5-hng5 e5 tak8 sou2-chai7 choe3-kang. Bi2-kok si7 se3-kai3 e5 chit8 kak, Ka-na2-tai7 put-ko3 ia7-si7 se3-kai3 e5 chit8 e5 sio2 kak na7-tiaN7. Choan5 se3-kai3 tioh8 long2 tit-tioh8 hok-im, lan2 ia7 chai 몬se3-kai3 si7 choe3-kang e5 sou2-chai7몭, it-teng7 tioh8 kau3 ti7 se3-kai3 e5 tak8 sou2-chai7 khi3, kang-chok chi2-u7 chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 chit kak kau3 hit kak, tong5-si5 ti7 choan5 se3-kai3 lai5 choe3.

Hun-chhau2 kong-si ti7 chin hng7 e5 sou2-chai7 ia7 u7 in e5 tai7-li2-tiam3, u7 kui2-na7-pah ban7 e5 hun sang3 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 teh hou7 lang5 chiah8. Che m7-si7 kong2 ti7 kok-lai7 i2-keng u7 kau3-giah8 e5 hun, chhun e5 chiah sang3 tui3 goa7-kok khi3, ti7 kok-lai7 hit e5 su-iau3 si7 koh-khah choe7 e5 ---- tek8-piat8 hian7-si5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khai-si2 teh chiah8 hun ---- in-ui7 an2-ni kok-lai7 e5 su-iau3 si7 koh khah choe7. Chong2-si7 hun-chhau2 kong-si i2-keng phai3 in e5 lang5 khi3 goa7-kok, in-ui7 in su-iau3 sin e5 chhi7-tiuN5. In pi2 lan2 koh khah u7 ti3-hui7, ui7-tioh8 beh sit8-heng5 Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-oe7, tek-khak tioh8 chin7-liong7 hak8-sip8 in. Lan2 beh ti7 kok-lai7 theng3-hau7 kau3 kok-lai7 e5 kang-chok oan5-seng5 liau2-au7 chiah chhut-khi3, che m7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3, I ai3 lan2 khi3 choan5 se3-kai3, siang5-si5 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 sou2-chai7 khai-si2 kang-chok.

Li2 m7 siong-sin3 tioh8 khi3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7, chiu7-si7 teh kong2, Po2-lo5 sou2 choe3 e5 m7-tioh8, Po2-lo5 m7 eng-kai kau3 Au-chiu lang5 hia khi3 thoan5-to7, i eng-kai tioh8 ti7 i e5 kok-lai7, thoan5 hok-im chiah tioh8. Na7 si7 an2-ni, li2 kho2-leng5 iau2 boe7 sin3 Siong7-te3. Li2 na7 m7 siong-sin3 tioh8 khi3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7, li2 chiu7-si7 bo5 ai3 tit-kiu3 e5 lang5.

PAI5 TI7 AU7-BIN7 E5 LANG5

Li2 kiam2 oe7 ki3-tit, Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok chhi7 5 chheng lang5 e5 kou3-su7 mah? Li2 oe7 ki3-tit, I chaiN2-iuN7 kio3 in che7 loh8-khi3, chit8-pai2 chit8-pai2 che7 ho2-se3 ti7 chhiN-chhui3 e5 chhau2-pou7. I theh8 piaN2 kap hi5, chiok-sia7 liau2-au7 chiu7 peh hou7 I e5 hak8-seng. Hak8-seng theh8 piaN2 kap hi5, kau3 ti7 choe3 thau5-cheng5 hit pai5, khai-si2 chiong piaN2 kap hi5 long2 pun hou7 hit pai5 e5 lang5. Au7-lai5 in koh to3-tng2 kau3 Ia5-sou hia theh8 piaN2 kap hi5, te7 2 pai2 koh pun hou7 choe3 thau5-cheng5 siang5 hit pai5 e5 lang5.

Bo5! Long2 m7-si7 an2-ni. In na7 an2-ni choe3, au7-bin7 hiah e5 lang5 tek-khak oe7 khia7-khi2 lai5 kong2: 몮ChhiaN2 theh8 kau3 goan2 chia lai5, goan2 long2 bo5 tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8, goan2 ti7 chia teh iau, goan2 iau2 bo5 tit-tioh8 thau5 chit8 pai5 i2-cheng5, siaN2-su7 hiah e5 choe3 thau5-cheng5 pai5 e5 lang5 chiu7 tit-tioh8 te7 2 pai2 nih?몯

In sou2 kong2 e5 chin tioh8, lan2 tiam3 ti7 kok-lai7 si7 teh hiong2-siu7 te7 2 pai2 e5 hok-khi3. Chong2-si7 iau2 u7 choe7-choe7 goa7-kok lang5 lian5 thau5 1 pai2 e5 hok-khi3 to iau2-boe7 tit-tioh8. Lan2 hian7-chai7 teh kong2-khi2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok te7 2 pai2 koh lai5 e5 su7, chong2-si7 iau2 u7 chin choe7 lang5 lian5 Ia5-sou thau5 1 pai2 lai5 e5 siau-sit to iau2 boe7 thiaN-tioh8. SiaN2-su7 u7 lang5 iau2 boe7 thiaN-tioh8 thau5 chit8 pai2 i2-cheng5, lan2 chiu7 ti7 chia thiaN chin choe7 pai2 nih? Li2 chai-iaN2 goa2 sou2 teh choe3 e5 su7, chiu7 si7 tak8 lang5 iau2 boe7 tit-tioh8 thau5 chit8 pai2 e5 pang-chan7 i2-cheng5 sou2 u7 5000 lang5 tiong e5 to2 chit8 e5, bo5-lun7 hu7-jin5-lang5, gin2-na2, long2 m7 eng-kai tit-tioh8 te7 2 pai2 e5 pang-chan7.

Niu5-sit8 e5 hun-phoe3 eng-kai tioh8 choat8-tui3 kong-to7, chong2-si7 chin kong-peng5 e5 su7, sit8-chai7 chin chio2, u7 e5 kau3-hoe7 long2 bo5 teh an2-ni choe3. In bo5 khoaN3-tang7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7 chhin-chhiuN7 khoaN3-tang7 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 chit8-iuN7.

