THAU5 CHIT8 E5 LI2-IU5

Khi2-thau5 goa2 siuN7 I si7 beh kong2 khi3 kang-chok e5 iau3-kin2, I si7 beh kong2, lan2 iau2 boe7 choe3 sim2-mih8 i2-cheng5, tek-khak tioh8 tai7-seng chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3.

