U7 chit8 e5 si5-tai7 si7 tek-khak tioh8 oan5-seng5 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7, siaN2-su7 ti7 lan2 chit e5 si5-tai7 bo5 beh khi3 choe3 nih? SiaN2-su7 tioh8 lau5 kau3 ti7 au7 se3-tai7 nih? Cheng5 se3-tai7 e5 lang5 na7 bo5 cho3, au7 se3-tai7 e5 lang5 kho2-leng5 ia7 boe7 cho3, sou2-i2 chit hang7 su7 tek-khak tioh8 oan5-seng5. Goa2 kong2, 몮Tioh8 ti7 chit se3-tai7 tiong oan5-seng5몯. SiaN2-su7 lan2 ka-ki7 tui3 chiah e5 su7 long2 bo5 teh koan-sim nih? Siat-su2 lan2 na7 goan7-i3, lan2 chiu7 oe7 thang choe3 chit e5 su7.

