HIAN7-CHAI7 E5 HONG-HOAT

Kim-jit8 lan2 su2-iong7 bo5-soaN3 tian7-tai5, lan2 u7 chiong tian7-tai5 siat ti7 choan5 se3-kai3, thong koe3 chiah e5 tian7-tai5 lan2 thang chiong hok-im thoan5 chhut-khi3, an2-ni lan2 ti7 te2-te2 e5 si5-kan lai7 chiu7 oe7 thang tat8 kau3 ti7 kui2-na7 ni5 ku2 chiah oe7 thang kau3 chin hng7 e5 sou2-chai7.

