LAN2 KAP INN7-KAU3 E5 CHOK-CHIAN3 OE7 TEK-SENG3 BOE7?

ChhiaN2 lan2 khoaN3 Lo5-ma2 10 chiuN, 13-15 chat: 몮In-ui7 kiN3-na7 kiu5-kio3 Chu2 e5 mia5 e5 lang5 beh tit-tioh8 kiu3. Chong2-si7 in sou2 iau2-be7 sin3 e5, thai2-tho2 oe7 kiu5-kio3 I? Sou2 be7 thiaN-kiN3 e5, thai2-tho2 oe7 sin3 I? Na7 bo5 lang5 thoan5, thai2-tho2 oe7 thiaN-kiN3? Na7 m7 si7 hong7-chhe, thai2-tho2 oe7 thoan5? Chiau3 sou2 ki3-chai3 kong2, Thoan5 chiah e5 ho2-su7 e5 hok-im e5, in e5 kha-pou7 sui2 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7!몯

Lan2 u7 khoaN3-tioh8 4 ku3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 몮thai2-tho2몯; tai7-seng u7 2 ku3 iok-sok e5 oe7, chiu7-si7 몮kiu5-kio3몯 kap 몮tit-tioh8 kiu3.몯 Chong2-si7 beh kiu5-kio3, in tek-khak tioh8 sin3, ui7-tioh8 beh sin3, in tek-khak tioh8 thiaN, ui7-tioh8 beh thiaN, tioh8 ai3 u7 lang5 kong2, ui7-tioh8 beh kong2, tioh8 u7 lang5 siu7 chhe-phai3. Siat-su2 lan2 chhe-phai3 soan-kau3-su, in oe7 khi3 kong2, in na7 kong2, hiah e5 bi7-sin3-chia2 oe7 tui3 thiaN lai5 sin3, na7 sin3, in chiu7 oe7 kiu5-kio3, in na7 kiu5-kio3, in chiu7 beh tit-tioh8 kiu3. Chong2-si7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 chiu7-si7 lan2 tioh8 chhe-phai3 lang5 khi3 thoan5.

CHOE3 TIONG7-IAU3 E5 KANG-CHOK

Na7-si7 an2-ni sim2-mih8 si7 choe3 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok? Chiu7-si7 tioh8 sit8-heng5 Chu2 e5 beng7-leng7, chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 hiah e5 m7 bat thiaN-tioh8 e5 lang5. Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, che pi2 sim2-mih8 koh khah iau3-kin2 e5. 몮Lin2 tioh8 khi3 phou2 thiN-e7, thoan5 hok-im hou7 ban7 peh-siN3 thiaN몯 (Ma2-kho2 16 chiuN 15 chat).

Lan2 tioh8 eng7 chit e5 choe3 lan2 e5 leng5-seng3, teh sun7-than3 Seng3-keng ka3-si7, lan2 e5 kau3-li2 u7 kun-ku3 Seng3-keng, lan2 it-teng7 oe7 chiong se3-kai3 e5 thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it; lan2 tioh8 chu7-iu5 hong7-hian3 choe3 thoan5-to7 e5 lou7-eng7.

Hou7 hiah e5 bo5 teh koan-sim che su7 e5 lang5 khi3 choe3 in ka-ki7 e5 su7; chong2-si7 lan2 chiah e5 thiaN-kiN3 Siong7-te3 tiau3-beng7 e5 lang5, tioh8 chip8-tiong lan2 e5 it-chhe3 ti7 hok-im iau2 boe7 kau3 e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7-si7 chiong Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 hok-im thoan5 kau3 ti7 m7 bat thiaN-tioh8 hok-im e5 peh-siN3.

U7 chit8 koa2 bo5 thoan5-to7 jiat8-cheng5 e5 lang5, tui3 sou2 thiaN e5 to7-li2, siu7 kam2-tong7, chiah hong7-hian3 tam7-poh8. Sou2 piau2-hian7 e5 chin chio2, chong2-si7 ia7 oe7 thang chiong in e5 hong7-hian3 choe3 chit e5 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok. An2-ni chiu7 oe7 thang hou7 chit8 e5 sin e5 chng-sia7 a2-si7 chit e5 sin e5 kok-ka e5 lang5 tit-tioh8 hok-im. Ia7 u7 chit8 koa2 lang5 in-ui7 tui3 hian3-kim lai5 kiong-kip 50 mia5 a2-si7 100 mia5 e5 soan-kau3-su ti7 pat8 sou2-chai7 teh choe3 kang, tui3 an2-ni tit-tioh8 kong2 boe7 chhut-lai5 e5 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8. In hian7-chai7 teh ke3-ek8 beh hong7-hian3 kok khah choe7. Ia7 u7 choe7-choe7 bo5 khoaN3-tioh8 hok-im thoan5 kau3 phou2 thiN-e7 e5 iau3-kin2-seng3 e5 lang5, in ia7 hoaN-hi2 hong7-hian3. An2-ni choe3 chiu7 tui3 in ka-ki7 e5 sou2-chai7 sou2 beh choe3 e5 kang-chok ia7 bo5 ti3-kau3 khiam3-kheh chiah tioh8.

Lan2 u7 chit8 e5 chin toa7 koh iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok, ia7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 u7 kong2, 몮Goa2 beh tui3 li2 e5 chhiu2 tho2 i e5 huih.몯 Lan2 na7 bo5 thoan5 hok-im, chit ku3 oe7 tek-khak beh eng3-giam7 ti7 lan2. Siat-su2 Ban7-ong5 e5 Ong5 beh lai5 thong2-ti7, lan2 tek-khak tioh8 oan5-seng5 chit hang7 kang-chok. I chiong che su7 kau-tai3 lan2, lan2 beh hou7 I tan2 joa7-ku2 ah? Lan2 eng-kai tioh8 pang3-sak it-chhe3, chip8-tiong lan2 e5 kang-chok ti7 chit e5 toa7 bok8-phiau, tioh8 ti7 lan2 chit e5 si5-tai7 lai5 oan5-seng5, hou7 hok-im thoan5 kau3 se3-kai3 tak8 sou2-chai7.

Oh! goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, chhiaN2 iong5-un2 goa2 ti7 sou2 chhun e5 kui2-ni5 ku2 lai5 khou2-khng3 li2, chin7 it-chhe3 e5 hong-hoat chiong hok-im thoan5 chhut-khi3, in-ui7, che chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou lau5 hou7 kau3-hoe7 sou2 tioh8 choe3 tok8-it e5 kang-chok. Chit e5 kang-chok si7 hian7-si5 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok. Lan2 kiam2 u7 teh choe3 chit e5 su7? Lan2 tui3 chit e5 kang-chok kiam2 u7 teh lou2-lek8? Lan2 sou2 choe3 e5 u7 sim2-mih8 chin3-pou7 e5 piau2-hian7? Lan2 kap iN7-kau3 e5 tou3-cheng tiong u7 tek-seng3? Lan2 tioh8 lai5 khoaN3-mai7 leh.

CHOE7-CHOE7 KHIUNN-KHAU2 E5 LANG5 KAP CHNG-SIA7 LONG2 IAU2-BE7 THIANN TIOH8 HOK-IM

Li2 kiam2 chai ti7 lan2 e5 se3-kai3 nih u7 joa7-choe7 e5 khiuN-khau2? Goa2 ka7 li2 kong2, hian7-si5 chi3-chio2 u7 2974 khoan2 chu2-iau3 e5 gian5-gu2. Li2 kiam2 chai chiah e5 gian5-gu2 e5 tiong-kan kui2 chiong2 u7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7? Hian7-si5 chi2-u7 1202 chiong2 na7-tiaN7, an2-ni iau2 u7 joa7 choe7 e5 gian5-gu2 bo5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7? Iau2 u7 1772 chiong2. ChhiaN2 li2 siuN7 khoaN3-mai7, iok u7 2000 ni5 e5 soan-kau3 kang-chok, chong2-si7 u7 1772 chiong2 e5 gian5-gu2, iau2 bo5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. Siong7-te3 tui3 chit khoan2 e5 cheng5-heng5 beh an2-choaN2 kong2 nih? 몮Sin3 si7 tui3 thiaN lai5, thiaN si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 lai5몯, in na7 bo5 thiaN thai2-tho2 oe7 sin3? Chong2-si7 in na7 bo5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, an2-ni in beh tui3 ta2-loh8 thang tit-tioh8 kiu3?

Chiau3 thong2-ke3, se3-kai3 iau2 u7 2000 e5 bin5-chok8, m7 bat thiaN tioh8 hok-im, lan2 ia7 i2-keng chai-iaN2 in toa3 ti7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7. Goa2 ai3 chhiaN2 lin2 lai5 koan-sim, ai3 lin2 lai5 jin7-bat in, ia7 tioh8 chai ti7 in e5 tiong-kan iau2 bo5 soan-kau3-su teh kang-chok. In long2 iau2 bo5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, ki5-sit8 in long2 m7 bat thiaN-kiN3 Ia5-sou e5 mia5-ji7.

Ti7 Sin-ki-ni5-a2 u7 626 e5 bin5-chok8, Lam5-iuN5-to2-su7 u7 521 e5, Hui-chiu u7 350 e5, Lam5 Bi2-chiu u7 300 e5, O3-tai7-li7-a u7 200 e5 (goan5-chu7 bin5-chok8), In3-tou7 u7 100 e5, Oat8-lam5 u7 60 e5, Hui-lip8-pin u7 60 e5. In iau2 m7 bat Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 hok-im, iau2 ti7 ou-am3 e5 tiong-kan.

Kan-taN ti7 Pa-se u7 100 goa7 chiong2 sun5 In3-te7-an lang5 150 ban7, Phou-lu7-ui5-a u7 100 ban7 e5 In3-te7-an lang5, Pi3-lo2 u7 250 ban7, Ko-lun5-pi2-a u7 10 ban7 e5. chiah e5 In3-te7-an lang5 toa7-pou7-hun7 long2 iau2 tiam3 ti7 ia2-ban5 e5 goan5-si2 chong7-thai7, ki5-thaN iau2 u7 50 ban7 e5 tiam3 ti7 ko-san e5 In3-te7-an lang5, ti7 poaN3 bun5-beng5 e5 toe7-tai3.

Tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7-thang hou7 in tit-tioh8 hok-im? Chiu7-si7 tioh8 oa2-kho3 lan2 cheng3 kau3-hoe7 e5 chheng-lian5 lang5, Seng3-keng hak8-iN7, kap Sin5 hak8-iN7. Chheng-lian5 lang5 tioh8 khi3, in-ui7 tak8 sou2-chai7 e5 soan-kau3 thoan5-the2 long2 teh iau3-kiu5 jin5-chai5.

Che chiu7-si7 goa2 khi3 Eng-kok tui3 chheng-lian5 lang5 kong2 to7-li2 e5 ian5-kou3, kiat-ko2 u7 1200 mia5 e5 chi3-goan7 chia2 chhut-lai5. Che ia7 si7 goa2 pian3 kiaN5 Bi2-kok kap Ka-na2-tai7 e5 goan5-in. 몮Choe3 kang e5 lang5 chio2몯, lan2 su-iau3 koh khah choe7 lang5, che chiu7-si7 goa2 hong7-hian3 ka-ki7 choe3 soan-kau3-su kang-chok e5 goan5-in. Hok-im tek-khak tioh8 thoan5 kau3 ti7 choan5 se3-kai3. Goan2 sou2 u7 e5 ng3-bang7 si7 he7 ti7 chheng-lian5 lang5, in na7 m7 khi3, chit e5 kang-chok chiu7 bo5 lang5 ai3 khi3 choe3 lah. Siong7-te3 teh keng2-tiau3 chheng-lian5 lang5, chheng-lian5 eng-kai tioh8 in3-tap.

Lan2 oe7 ki3-tit, Ia5-sou sou2 u7 e5 hak8-seng long2 si7 chheng-lian5 lang5. Ia5-sou ti7 in chheng-lian5 e5 si5-chun7 keng2-tiau3 in, ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 bo5 kou3 in e5 siN3-mia7 khi3 thoan5. Lan2 tioh8 oh8 in, tioh8 chiong lan2 choe3 ho2 e5 hian3 chhut-lai5. Siong7-te3 chi2-u7 chit8 e5 tok8-siN kiaN2, chong2-si7 iu5-goan5 chhe I choe3 soan-kau3-su, sou2-i2 lan2 kiam2 thang khah su mah?

Choe7-choe7 lang5 bat thak8 tioh8, Li2-bun5-su-tun3, Mou5-hoat, Khia-li2, Ia5-tek-sun teng2 choe7-choe7 soan-kau3-su e5 kou3-su7, in thak8 liau2-au7 chiu7 chi3-goan7, khi3 thoan5 to7-li2. Peng5-iu2! Hian7-chai7 u7 choe7-choe7 thoan5-to7 e5 ki-koan teh bou7-chip8 lang5 khi3 thoan5 to7-li2, iau2 u7 choe7-choe7 bin5-chok8 bo5 tit-tioh8 hok-im, SiaN2-su7 bo5 beh khi3 thoan5?

Goa2 ti7 Sou-bun5-tap-lah e5 si5, u7 chit8 pai2 thiaN-kiN3 u7 chit8 e5 siaN5-chhi7, iau2 m7-bat u7 thoan5-kau3-chia2 khi3, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 kiaN5 koe3 toa7 chhiu7-na5 kau3 hit e5 sou2-chai7, goa2 long2 bo5 boe7 ki3-tit, tng-si5 goa2 jip8 hit e5 siaN5-mng5 e5 kam2-tong7. Siat-su2 goa2 hian7-chai7 iau2-ku2 si7 chit8 e5 chheng-lian5 lang5, goa2 tek-khak bo5 ai3 kau3 ti7 pat8-lang5 i2-keng khi3 choe3 kang e5 sou2-chai7. Goa2 it-teng7 beh chhin-chhiuN7 Li2-bun5-su-tun3 chit8-iuN7, kau3 ti7 sin e5 tiuN5-sou2, goa2 it-teng7 beh hoan-ek8 Seng3-keng, chiong hok-im thoan5 hou7 hiah e5 peh-siN3, goa2 beh hoe3 chit8 e5 khai-thok-chia2.

SiaN2-su7 li2 tiam3 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 sou2-chai7 teh long7-hui3 li2 e5 oah8-mia7? Li2 thang kau3 ti7 bo5 lang5 bat khi3 thoan5 hok-im e5 sou2-chai7, chiong li2 e5 oah8-mia7 tau5-chu ti7 chin-chiaN3 u7 ke3-tat8 e5 ta7-chi3. Li2 na7 khi3, li2 beh tit-tioh8 koh khah toa7 e5 sou2-chai7. SiaN2-su7 bo5 beh hou7 li2 e5 seng-oah8 koh khah u7 i3-gi7? Li2 ia7 thang choe3 chit8 e5 khai-thok-chia2 khi3 thoan5 to7-li2.

Oh! goa2 chai li2 sou2 beh kong2 e5, in-ui7 goa2 i2-keng thiaN kui2-na7 pian3, li2 in2-iong7 Su3-tou5-heng5-toan7 1 chiuN 8 chat, chong2-si7 li2 in2-iong7 liau2 m7 tioh8, li2 e5 in2-iong7 si7 an2-ni houN3? 몮Lin2 tioh8 tai7-seng ti7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2, jian5-au7 ti7 Iu5-thai3, jian5-au7 ti7 Sat-ma2-li7-a i2-kip choan5-toe7 tit8-kau3 toe7-kek8.몯 Na7-si7 chit chat Seng3-keng e5 i3-su3 m7-si7 an2-ni kai2-sek. Hian7-chai7 goa2 lai5 kai2-sek hou7 li2 thiaN, 몮li2 tioh8 ui7-tioh8 goa2 choe3 kan-cheng3 ti7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 kap Iu5-thai3, koh ti7 Sat-ma2-li7-a tit8-kau3 toe7-kek8,몯 m7-si7 몮tai7-seng몯, si7 몮koh ti7몯, an2-ni chit ji7 몮koh ti7몯 si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3? Chiu7-si7 siang7-si5 e5 i3-su3. OaN7 chit8 ku3 oe7 lai5 kong2: Lan2 chit8 bin7 ti7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 thoan5 hok-im, siang7-si5 ia7 tioh8 ti7 Iu5-thai3, Sat-ma2-li7-a kau3 toe7-kek8 thoan5 hok-im. M7-si7 beh khi3 pat8-ui7 kang-chok i2-cheng5, tioh8 tai7-seng choe3-oan5 chit peng5 e5 kang-chok, lan2 tioh8 siang7-si5 ti7 2 e5 sou2-chai7 kang-chok, ti7 pun2-kok kap goa7-kok tioh8 siang7-si5 khai-si2 choe3 chiah tioh8.

PUN2-KOK A2-SI7 GOA7-KOK HIT-PENG5?

Li2 thiaN chiah e5 oe7 u7 sim2-mih8 kam2-siong2? Tui3 bo5-soaN3-tian7 e5 hoat-beng5 liau2-au7, bo5-lun7 toa3 ti7 joa7 hng7 e5 sou2-chai7, na7 khui siu-im-ki, chiu7 long2 oe7 thiaN-tioh8 hok-im chiat-bok8. Chong2-si7 goa2 ia7 bat khi3 kau3 choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7, hia u7 kui2 na7 pah ban7 e5 lang5, long2 bo5 bo5-soaN3-tian7, ia7 bo5 kong2-pou3 tian7-tai5, bo5 siu-im-ki. Hiah e5 lang5 chin ai3 thiaN hok-im, ia7 bo5 pan7-hoat. SiaN2-su7 hiah-nih koan-sim ti7 pun2-kok e5 lang5, ai7 tui3 pat8 sou2-chai7, tui3 koh khah hng7 e5 lang5 chiu7 long2 bo5 koan-sim?

Goa2 chin7 ai3 eng7 koh khah choe7 e5 chiN5 ti7 chhut-pan2, eng7 goa7-kok oe7 sia2-chheh, tu5-khi3 an2-ni, in chiu7 bo5 sim2-mih8 thang thak8. Ti7 pun2-kok hok-im e5 chheh siong5-siong5 hou7 lang5 ku7-choat8, na7-si7 ti7 hia, chiau3 goa2 sou2 chai, m7-bat tu2-tioh8 lih-phoa3 toaN-tiuN a2-si7 in sou2 chih-tioh8 e5 sio2-chheh. In chin u7 le2-sou3 lai5 chiap-siu7 koh kam2-sia7 hit e5 sang3 hou7 I e5 lang5, jian5-au7 bo5-lun7 ti7 tian7-chhia, kong-liong7 khi3-chhia a2-si7 hoe2-chhia, in long2 chin hoaN-hi2 sui5-si5 lai5 thak8. Goa2 ti7 Se-pan-ga5 e5 si5, goa2 e5 chhia si5-siong5 hou7 chin choe7 lam5-lu2 ui5-ui5 leh, in-ui7 goa2 teh pun hok-im thoan5-toaN, in ui7-tioh8 ai3 tit-tioh8 hok-im e5 thoan5-toaN chiu7 chhun chhut in e5 chhiu2 lai5 tho2. Goa2 kam2-kak in hiah-nih jiat8-sim teh tho2, ai3 chai-iaN2 hit e5 hok-im e5 thoan5-toaN, sou2 beh ka7 in kong2 e5 su7.

Siat-su2 na7 u7 chit8 tai5 chhia, chai3 hok-im thoan5-toaN, kau3 moa2-moa2 tui3 Hoat-kok sai2 kau3 I2-tai7-li7, a2-si7 tui3 Kou2-pa kau3 Hai2-te7, chit8 lou7 it-tit8 pun, kan-taN an2-ni choe3 chiu7 ho2, tek-khak oe7 hou7 chin-choe7 lang5 chin3-jip8 ti7 eng2-oah8. Sim7-chi3 u7 lang5 boe7 hiau2 eng7 in e5 oe7 kang2-to7, ia7 oe7 thang eng7 chit e5 hong-hoat lai5 thoan5-to7. Siong7-te3 tek-khak beh eng7 bun5-ji7 thoan5-to7 lai5 choe3-kang, che si7 goa2 eng7 chin-choe7 chiN5 ti7 chit hong-bin7 e5 goan5-in. Goa2 u7 kam2-kak tioh8, bo5 pi2 pun hok-im sio2-chheh koh khah u7 hau7-ko2 e5 thoan5-to7. Chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 ti7 Sou-ngou5, Au-chiu, Lam5-bi2 teng2 e5 sou2-chai7, in-ui7 lan5 chin ai3 thak8. Goa2 u7 chin-choe7 ka-ki7 e5 chheh hoan-ek8 choe3 Sou-ngou5 e5 oe7, ia7 u7 hoan-ek8 choe3 35 chiong2 ki5-thaN e5 oe7, si3-soaN3 ti7 kui2-na7 chheng-ban7 lang5 e5 tiong-kan, ia7 hit e5 hau7-ko2 chin toa7.

ChhiaN2 li2 siuN7 khoaN3, ti7 pun2-kok u7 choe7-choe7 e5 thoan5-the2 teh ke3-ek8 beh chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 thoan5 hok-im, chong2-si7 chin chio2 lang5 siuN7 kau3 ti7 goa7-kok. In siuN7 hiah e5 m7-si7 in sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5 kang, lan2 chi2-u7 teh siuN7 kok-lai7 e5 kang-chok, soa3 boe7 ki3-tit hiah e5 goa7-kok e5 kang-chok. ChhiaN2 mng7 na7 u7 10 e5 lang5 beh kng chit8 ki chha5, chit8 thau5 u7 9 e5, leng7-goa7 chit8 thau5 chi2-u7 chit8 e5, an2-ni kiam2 oe7 eng7-tit? SiaN2-su7 li2 bo5 beh pang-chan7 hit thau5 chi2-u7 1 e5 lang5 teh kng e5 nih? Che chiu7-si7 goa7-kok e5 kang-chok su-iau3 lan2 khi3 pang-chan7 e5 goan5-in.

SANN E5 BO5 SANN-TANG5 E5 LANG5

Goa2 chin ai3 kong2 khi2 saN e5 bo5 saN-tang5 e5 lang5. Thau5 chit8 e5 si7 chhe-phai3-chia2, te7 2 e5 si7 ki5-to2 e5, te7 3 e5 si7 boe7 thang khiam3-chio2 e5, chiu7-si7 siu7 chhe-phai3 e5 lang5, 3 e5 long2 si7 chin su-iau3 e5.

Beh chhe-phai3 lang5 tek-khak tioh8 u7 chiN5, siat-su2 li2 na7 boe7 tang3 khi3, peng5-iu2, kiam2-chhai2 Siong7-te3 si7 ai3 li2 choe3 chit8 e5 chhe-phai3-chia2. Na7 an2-ni li2 tioh8 chhoe7 chit8 lang5 thoe3 li2 khi3, li2 sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5 chiu7-si7 than3-chiN5, eng7 chiN5 lai5 chi-chhi5 lang5 chhut-khi3 thoan5 hok-im. Li2 na7 hoaN-hi2 an2-ni lai5 choe3, li2 sou2 beh tit-tioh8 e5 po3-siuN2 kap i si7 siang7 chit8-iuN7 e5.

Koh lai5 chiu7-si7 ki5-to2 e5 lang5, kiam2-chhai2 li2 boe7 thang than3-chiN5, li2 sou2 than3 e5 chiN5 chi2-u7 oe7 thang kiong-kip li2 ka-ki7 e5 su-iau3. An2-ni li2 boe7 thang chhe-phai3 pat8-lang5 khi3, li2 oe7 thang chiaN5-choe3 chit8 e5 ki5-to2 e5 lang5, tak8-jit8 eng7 li2 sio2-khoa2 e5 si5-kan lai5 ui7-tioh8 Hui-chiu, In3-tou7 kap Tiong-kok lai5 ki5-to2, li2 ia7 oe7 thang tit-tioh8 soan-kau3-su e5 mia5-toaN, jian5-au7 ui7-tioh8 in ki5-to2. Li2 na7 siuN7 beh siam2-pi7 li2 e5 chek-jim7, chai-e7 tek-khak beh lim5-kau3 li2. Siat-su2 li2 na7 ui7-tioh8 hiah e5 khi3 goa7-kok e5 lang5 tiong-sit8 lai5 ki5-to2, li2 ia7 oe7 thang tit-tioh8 po3-siuN2, an2-ni li2 chiu7 u7 hun7 ti7 in e5 kang-chok.

Iau2 u7 chit8 khoan2 chiu7-si7 siu7 chhe-phai3 e5 lang5. Siat-su2 li2 e5 sin-khu kian7-khong koh iong2-chong3, chiu7 tioh8 siu7 hun3-lian5, keng-koe3 chun2-pi7 liau2-au7 thang khi3 thoan5 hok-im. Li2 ui7-tioh8 it-seng e5 kang-chok ki5-to2 e5 si5, u7 chit8 chiong2 e5 khui3-lat8 lim5-kau3 li2, li2 chiu7 oe7 thang sui5-si5 beng5-pek8. Siong7-te3 si7 teh kio3 li2, goa2 ai3 li2 chham-ka ti7 se3-kai3 choe3 ui2-tai7 e5 kang-chok. Siat-su2 li2 na7 oe7 thang khi3, si7 bo5 u7 pi2 chit e5 koh khah ho2 e5. Soan-kau3-su si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 tui3-tiong7, si7 kau3-hoe7 e5 po2-poe3. Li2 chiu7 u7 hun7 ti7 toe7-chiuN7 choe3 ho2 e5 kang-chok.

Chit si5 si7 tioh8 cho3 kang e5 si5-chun7----tioh8 oan5-seng5 chit e5 bi7 oan5-seng5 e5 kang-chok. 몮Bo5 u7 thoan5-to7 e5, thai2-tho2 oe7 thiaN-kiN3, bo5 u7 hong7-chhe, thai2-tho2 oe7 thoan5 to7-li2 nih?몯 Lan2 kap iN7-kau3 chok-chian3 tiong oe7 tek-seng3 boe7? ChhiaN2 li2 ka-ki7 lai5 in3-tap che su7.

 
TE7 7 CHIUNN

SIANN2-SU7 KAU3-HOE7 TUI3 SE3-KAI3 E5 THOAN5-TO7 SIT-PAI7?

ChhiaN2 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. Iok-han7 Hok-im 4 chiuN 35 chat, 몮Lin2 kiam2 bo5 kong2, Iau2 u7 si3-geh8-jit8, chiu7 siu-koah e5 si5 kau3 mah? Goa2 ka7 lin2 kong2, kiah8 bak8 khoaN3 hng5, i2-keng sek8, thang koah lah.몯 Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, goa2 thak8 kau3 chiah e5 oe7 e5 si5, goa2 e5 sim chiu7 jiat8 khi2-lai5. Chit e5 Seng3-keng chat sit8-chai7 chin sek-hap8 ti7 kin-a2-jit8.

Tui3 Ia5-sou ka7 lan2 kong2, Tioh8 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, i2-lai5 i2-keng beh koe3 2000 ni5 lah, chong2-si7 iau2 u7 2000 e5 bin5-chok8 m7-bat thiaN tioh8 hok-im. Koh u7 kui2-na7 pah-ban7 lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 Tiong-kok, In3-tou7 teng2-teng2 e5 kok-ka iu5-goan5 u7 chin choe7 lang5 iau2 boe7 thiaN-tioh8 hok-im. U7 ou-bin7 lang5, ng5-bin7 lang5, chhiah-sek lang5----iau2 u7 chin choe7 boe7 bat thiaN Ki-tok e5 mia5. Chi3-chio2 ti7 se3-kan 30 ek e5 jin5-khau2 e5 tiong-kan, 100 hun chi 65 e5 lang5 iau2-boe7 chiap-siu7 hok-im.

Siong7-te3 m7 na7 beng7-leng7, I u7 toa7 koan5-leng5. Sou2-i2 lan2 thang oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 leng5-lek8 khi3 choe3. I boe7 kio3 lan2 khi3 choe3 hiah e5 put-kho2-leng5 e5 su7. Hok-im tek-khak tioh8 thoan5 kau3 ban7-pang.몯 SiaN2-su7 kau3 hian7-chai7 iau2 boe7 oan5-seng5 nih?

Te7 1----In-ui7 u7 hok-im e5 tui3-tek8.

Lan2 kin-a2-jit8 u7 tu2-tioh8 chin hiong5-beng2 i2-cheng5 m7-bat u7 e5 tui3-tek8, sou2-i2 u7 si5 lan2 kam2-kak tioh8 kiam2 oe7 iaN5 koe3 in. chia u7 3 hang7 tai7-chi3 lan2 tioh8 kap in tou3-cheng, chiu7-si7 kok-ka chu2-gi7, iN7-kau3, kiong7-san2 chu2-gi7.

Kok-ka chu2-gi7chhut-hian7 ti7 toa7 pou7-hun7 e5 kok-ka. Chit hang7 tui3 soan-kau3-su e5 kang-chok cheng7-ka choe7-choe7 e5 khun3-lan5. I e5 khau2-ho7 si7 몮Hui-chiu si7 Hui-chiu lang5 e5, In3-tou7 si7 In3-tou7 lang5 e5, Tiong-kok si7 Tiong-kok lang5 e5.몯 In koat-teng7 beh koaN2-chhut peh8-bin7 lang5, eng7 giau5-gi5 e5 bak8-chiu khoaN3 goa7-kok-lang5, sim7-chi3 soan-kau3-su ia7 bo5 siu7 hoan-geng5.

IN7-kau3 siong5-siong5 si7 hok-im e5 tui3-tek8, tek8-piat8 si7 Hoe5-hoe5-kau3 kap Thian-chu2-kau3, nng7-hang7 long2 bo5 hou7 lang5 u7 chu7-iu5. Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 se3-lek8 khah jiok8 e5 si5, in chiu7 iong5-un2 chu7-iu5. Chong2-si7 in e5 se3-lek8 na7 kiong5 khi2-lai5, in chiu7 piN3-choe3 tok8-chhai5-chia2, Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 siu7 ap-pek khun3-tiok8, i2-kip sun5-kau3. Thian-chu2-kau3 long2 bo5 tam7-poh8-a2 e5 lin5-bin2, na7 si7 Ki-tok-kau3 si7 i5-it siong-sin3 koh sit8-heng5 chu7-iu5 e5 chong-kau3.

Kiong7-san2 chu2-gi7 si7 Sat-tan3 sou2 chhong3-cho7, hoat-beng5, choe3 chan5-jim2 e5 bu2-khi3. I pi2 ki5-thaN sim2-mih8 chu2-gi7 koh khah kin2 hoat-tian2, ia7 tiam3 ti7 mui2 chit8 e5 kok-ka teh kong-kek Ki-tok-kau3. Kiong7-san2 chu2-gi7 teh khoa-khau2 kan-ta ti7 Lam5 Bi2-chiu chiu7 u7 100 ban7 lang5 teh sin3. Chit e5 siu7 sia5-sin5 sou2 kek-tong7 e5, bo5 sin3 Siong7-te3 e5 un7-tong7, si7 choat8-tui3 put-kho2-leng5 tho3-hiap8 e5. In e5 thih-bou7 toan7-choat8 it-chhe3 kap lai7-bin7, chou2-chi2 thoan5 hok-im.

I2-siong7 chit 3 hang7 si7 hok-im e5 tui3-tek8, sui-jian5 u7 chiah e5 hoan2-tui3, lan2 ia7 tioh8 chin3-cheng5, sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7. 몮Goa2 i2-keng hou7 lin2 u7 koan5 thang tah8 choa5 kap giat-a2-thang5, koh iaN5-ke3 tui3-tek8 long2-chong2 e5 khui3-lat8; koat-toan3 bo5 chit8-hang7 oe7 hai7 tioh8 lin2.몯 (Lou7-ka 10 chiuN 19 chat) Ti7 hok-im e5 lai7-bin7 u7 leng5-lek8, oe7 thang iaN5 koe3 it-chhe3 e5 tui3-tek8, koh chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3. 몮In-ui7 goa2 bo5 liah8 hok-im choe3 kian3-siau3, in-ui7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5 beh kiu3 long2-chong2 sin3 e5 lang5.몯 (Lo5-ma2 1 chiuN 16 chat)

Te7 2----In-ui7 lan2 kiong5-tiau kau3-iok8.

Goa2 chhim-sin3 kau3-iok8, hak8-hau7 si7 chin su-iau3 e5, in-ui7 lang5 thang tui3 che pou2-chhiong in sou2 khiam3-kheh e5.U7 lang5 si7 thian-chai5, chhin-chhiuN7 Bou7-tek (Moody) Hui-ni2-pok (Philpott) kap Kiap-pho2-che5 Su2-bit8-su (Gipsy Smith), in bo5-lun7 u7 siu7 kau3-iok8 a2 bo5 long2 oe7 seng5-kong. Kin-a2-jit8 u7 lang5 khoaN3 pit8-giap8 cheng3-su choe3 iau3-kin2, tit-tioh8 hak8-ui7 choe3 kong-eng5, chong2-si7 goa2 ia7 chai sui-jian5 u7 hak8-ui7 iau2 u7 lang5 boe7 thang choe3 sim2-mih8.

Hoat-lan5-sun (Franson) bat phai3 100 e5 sin e5 soan-kau3-su hou7 Te3 Tek-seng (Hudson Taylor). Hiah e5 soan-kau3-su si7 bo5 siu7 kau3-iok8 e5, u7 e5 chi2-u7 siu7 chit8 sut8-sut8-a2 e5 kau3-iok8 na7-tiaN7.

Te3 Tek-seng khoaN3 tioh8 in e5 si5, chiu7 sia2 phoe chek-pi7 Hoat-lan5-sun kong2 m7 eng-kai sang3 in lai5. Chong2-si7 2 ni5 au7 i koh-chai3 sia2 phoe ka7 i kong2, i i2-keng u7 khoaN3-kiN3 in e5 kang-chok, in choe3 chin ho2 e5 kang, in-ui7 long2 si7 siu7 Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2 e5 lang5, Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 khau2-chai5 hou7 in koh su3-hok in e5 tioh8-boa5, i kong2, i ai3 koh khah choe7 chit khoan2 e5 lang5.

U7 chit8-pai2 goa2 tui3 chit8 e5 soan-kau3-su e5 chi3-goan7-chia2 kong2: 몮Li2 tioh8 chin7 li2 e5 sou2 oe7 khi3 siu7 kau3-iok8.몯 Chong2-si7 goa2 tu5-khi3 hit pai2 i2-goa7 m7-bat koh an2-ni kong2, in-ui7 iau2 u7 koh khah tiong7-iau3 e5 tiau5-kiaN7, u7 si5 kau3-iok8 oe7 chiaN5 choe3 gui5-hiam2-seng3 e5. Choe7-choe7 lang5 ui7-tioh8 beh tit-tioh8 hak8-su7, a2-si7 sek8-su7 e5 hak8-ui7, sin3-giong2 chiu7 leng2-tam7. U7 lang5 su-iau3 kau3-iok8, chong2-si7 u7 lang5 bo5 su-iau3, siu7 kau3-iok8 m7 si7 lang5-lang5 sou2 su-iau3 e5, tak8-lang5 long2 u7 ko3-jin5 tek e5 su7-cheng5.

Choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 m7 si7 chit8 e5 lang5 ti7 thau5-nau2 u7 sim2-mih8, si7 tioh8 khoaN3 i e5 sim-lai7 u7 sim2-mih8, chiah u7 sng3-siau3 e5. Sim2-pho2-sun kap Bou7-tek, bo5 siu7 sim2-mih8 kau3-iok8, chong2-si7 iu5-goan5 u7 ki-hoe7 ui7 Siong7-te3 choe3 kang. Choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 si7 tioh8 gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng, ki5-thaN it-chhe3 e5 si5, si7 te7 2 iau3-kin2 e5, I m7 ai3 lan2 sit-loh8 thoan5-to7 e5 iN7-siong7.

Siong7-te3 beh eng7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 in2-chhoa7 kap chi2-to7, lai5 kau3-iok8 lang5. Chong2-si7 I iu5-goan5 beh eng7 bo5 siu7 kau3-iok8 a2-si7 siu7 chit8 sut8-a2 kau3-iok8 e5 lang5. Toa7-pou7-hun7 e5 thoan5-the2 long2 kui-teng7, u7 siu7 koe3 ko-teng2 kau3-iok8, keng-koe3 3 ni5 e5 Seng3-keng kho3-theng5 e5 kau3-iok8, koh u7 chit8 ni5 e5 sit8-che3 kang-chok, chiah u7 sek-hap8 ti7 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang. Goa2 siuN7 che siuN7-hoat put-ko3 si7 hak8-hau7 hong-bin7 e5 siuN7-hoat, na7 bo5 tong-jian5 i tioh8 ai3 ti7 bou2 chit8 hong-bin7 khah u7 choan-bun5-tek chiah oe7 eng7-tit. Chong2-si7 sit8-che3 siong7 u7 chin choe7 bo5 siu7 ko-teng2 kau3-iok8 e5 lang5, iu5-goan5 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 tiong7-iong7 i.

Tng5 si5-ki5 siu7 kau3-iok8, tui3 thoan5 hok-im e5 jiat8-cheng5 u7 chin toa7 e5 sun2-sit, chin choe7 jiat8-sim ai3 khi3 thoan5-to7 kiu3 leng5-hun5 e5 lang5, ti7 hak7-iN7 a2-si7 Sin5-hak8-iN7 e5 ho2 khoan5-keng2 tiong sit-loh8 in e5 iN7-siong7. Chit8 e5 kang-lang5, keng-koe3 7, 8 geh8-jit8 e5 gian2-kiu3, u7 4, 5 hang7 e5 sit7-che3 keng-giam7 chiu7 i2-keng oe7 jiat8-sim ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 choe3-kang. Mui2-ni5 he7-thiN it-teng7 tioh8 chiong sou2 hak8-sip8 e5 eng3-iong7 ti7 sit8-che3 kang-chok chiah ho2. M7-thang kan-ta chiaN5 choe3 hak8-seng, tioh8 si5-siong5 u7 chek-kek8-tek e5 hok8-bu7 chiah ho2, tioh8 eng3-iong7 it-chhe3 e5 kho3-theng5 lai5 ko3-jin5 po3-to7, kian3-cheng3, a2-si7 kang2-to7, chin7-lat8 ui7 Chu2 choe3-kang. Na7 bo5 oe7 sit-loh8 khi2-thau5 e5 thiaN3, hoe2-jiat8 e5 sim oe7 siau-biat8, kiu3-leng5 e5 jiat8-cheng5 ia7 oe7 siau-bo5 khi3.

Choe7-choe7 hak8-seng pit-giap8, nia2 cheng3-su, tit-tioh8 hak8-su7 ui7 e5 si5, long2 teh siuN7 in e5 hak8-giap8 kiat-sok lah. Chong2-si7 goa2 ai3 kong2, hit si5 si7 tu2-tu2 khai-si2 e5 si5-chun7. In-ui7 hak8-hau7 si7 chi2-u7 teh ka3 lang5 tioh8 gian2-kiu3, i2-au7 in tioh8 kau3-iok8 ka-ki7, an2-ni chiu7 thang tit-tioh8 pi2 ti7 hak8-hau7 sou2 hak8-sip8 koh khah choe7, ia7 bu5-kiong-chin7. Hian7-si5 in thang choan-bun5 hoa3, thang soan2-tek ka-ki7 sou2 ai3 thak8 e5, jian5-au7 ti7 kang-chok hoan7-ui5 lai5 chaiN5 choe3 koan5-ui-chia2.

Chong2-si7 ia7 u7 m7 bat khi3 hak8-hau7 thak8 chheh e5 lang5, chiaN5 choe3 chhut-mia5 e5 leng2-to7-chia2, chhin-chhiuN7 Kiat-pho-che Su2-bit8-su, i lian5 tam7-poh8 kau3-iok8 to7 bo5, na7 si7 i ka-ki7 hak8-sip8, thak8 kap sia2. Li2 bat thiaN-tioh8 i teh kong2-oe7 mah? Li2 u7 chu3-i3 i sou2 kong2 e5 Eng-gu2 si7 long2 bo5 chho3-gou7 mah? Goa2 ti7 pun2-kok e5 si5 chit8-pai2 koh hit8-pai2 u7 thiaN-koe3 i kong2 oe7, m7-bat chit8 pai2 thiaN-kiN3 i ti7 bun5-hoat-siong7 u7 chho3-gou7. chong2-si7 chin choe7 tit-tioh8 hak8-su7 a2-si7 Sin5-hak8 Phok-su7 hak8-ui7 e5 lang5, in sui-jian5 siu7 koe3 hiah nih7 koan5 e5 kau3-iok8, iu5-goan5 siong5-siong5 m7-tioh8. Soan-kau3-su m7 si7 jin5-ui5 e5, si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 cho3 chhut e5, Siong7-te3 khoaN3 i u7 sek-hap8 si7 pi2 chun2-pi7 koh khah iau3-kin2. I ka-ki7 oe7 thang koat-teng7 ti7 ta2-loh8 chit8 hong-bin7 pi2-kau3 u7 hah8-eng7.

U7 chin choe7 chin ho2 e5 lang5, in-ui7 bo5 tit-tioh8 hak8-iN7 pit-giap8 e5 chu-keh, sou2-i2 boe7 thang jip8 Sin5-hak8-iN7, boe7 thang ti7 kau3-hoe7 kang-chok. Chong2-si7 chit8 e5 lang5 siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 keng2-tiau3 khi3 thoan5 hok-im, m7-bian2 siu7 hak8-bun7 e5 han7-che3. Siat-su2 na7 it-teng7 tioh8 oe7 hiau2 Hi-liap8-gu2 a2-si7 Hi-pek-lai5-gu2, an2-ni chiu7 bo5 lang5 oe7-thang khi3 thoan5 to7-li2.

Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Seng3-keng hak8-iN7 chiu7 san2-seng, u7 e5 tui3 long5-tiuN5 siu7 keng2-tiau3 lai5 hun3-lian7 ui7 Chu2 kang-chok, Koh chit8 hang7 chiu7-si7 kau3-phai3 koan-liam7, teh ui5-chhiuN5, kui-teng7 chin koan5 e5 hak8-hun che3-tou7, lai5 sit-loh8 choe7-choe7 chin ho2 koh jiat8-sim e5 kang-chok jin5-oan5. Chong2 u7 2 tiam2 si7 ui7 Chu2 choe3 kang e5, choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 chu-keh, chit8 hang7 chiu7-si7 Seng3-keng e5 choan5-pou7 ti3-sek koh chit8-hang7 si7 beh chaiN2-iuN7 su2-iong7 Seng3-keng.

Choe7-choe7 hak8-hau7 long2 bo5 ka3 hak8-seng tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 kang-chok, chi2-u7 koan3 thau5-nau2 e5 ti3-sek, ia7 bo5 ka3-si7 hak8-seng tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 sit8-che3-siong7 lai5 eng3-iong7.

Pou3-to7-hoe7, ti7 goa7-kok su-iau3, kap pun2-kok chit8-iuN7. Su7-sit8-siong7 goa7-kok si7 koh khah su-iau3, na7 an2-ni choe3, siu-seng5 it-teng7 oe7 koh khah choe7, tek8-piat8 ti7 se3-kai3 e5 kok toa7 tou-chhi7 lai5 ku2-heng5 e5 si5, oe7-thang tit-tioh8 koh khah toa7 e5 hau7-ko2. Goa2 ti7 Ho5-siok8 Tang In3-tou7 e5 si5, hia e5 soan-kau3-su bo5 ai3 goa2 ti7 pou3-to7-hoe7 tiong kong-khai chhiaN2 lang5 koat-chi3. Su7-sit8-siong goa2 e5 hoan-ek8 ka7 goa2 ku7-choat8 chit e5 su7, chong2-si7 goa2 chiu7 chin3-heng5. Siong7-te3 iu5-goan5 choe3 ki5-biau7 e5 kang-chok, tui3 hit-tiap8 i2-au7, in chiu7 chan3-seng5 goa2 e5 choe3-hoat. Tai7-chiong3 pou3-to7 ti7 goa7-kok si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 beh eng7, choe3 iu2-hau7 e5 hong-hoat. 

Te7 3----In-ui7 choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7 koaiN-mng5.

Sui-jian5 u7 choe7-choe7 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 mng5, i2-keng koaiN khi2-lai5, iau2 u7 khui teh e5 sou2-chai7, siaN2-su7 lan2 iau2 m7 jip8-khi3? SiaN2-su7 m7 eng7 khah choe7 e5 si5-kan ui7-tioh8 hiah e5 koaiN teh e5 mng5 ki5-to2? Li2 oe7 ki3-tit Po2-lo5 chit8 pai2 koh chit8 pai2 li7-khui koaiN teh e5 mng5, ia7 chin3-lip8 hiah e5 khui teh e5 mng5. Hian7-chai7 tak8 sou2-chai7 e5 mng5 long2 khui teh, beh hou7 lan2 li7-khui hiah e5 koaiN teh e5 mng5 lai5 jip8, ia7 theng3-hau7 Siong7-te3 khui hiah e5 koaiN teh e5 mng5 e5 jit8-chi2. I chai lan2 ti7 sim2-mih8 si5, ti7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 tioh8 choe3 kang, I oe7 ka7 lan2 ke3-ek8 kau3 chin ho2-se3.

Te7 4----Lan2 bo5 phai3 kau3-giah8 e5 soan-kau3-su.

Bun7-toe5 si7 kang-lang5 e5 sou3-giah8. Ti7 Tiong-kok e5 chhan5-hng5 toa7 koh khoah, long5-hu long2 tioh8 eng7 chhiu2 khi3 siu-seng5 it-chhe3 e5 ngou2-kok. Chong2-si7 in oe7 long2 siu kau3 liau2, siaN2-su7 neh? In-ui7 mui2 chit8 e5 lam5-lu2 lo2-iu3 chhut-khi3 choe3-kang. In e5 jin5-sou3 choe7, sou2 beh choe3 e5 kang long2 oe7 choe3 oan5.

Lan2 e5 Chu2 ia7 u7 chit-khoan2 e5 ke3-ek8, sou2-i2 I kong2: 몮thang siu-seng5 e5 si7 choe7, choe3-kang e5 si7 chio2, sou2-i2 lin2 tioh8 kiu5 hng5 chu2 pek kang khi3 ka7 I siu-seng5몯 (Ma2-thai3 9: 37, 38). Siat-su2 lan2 na7 u7 kau3-giah8 e5 kang-lang5, kang chiu7 choe3 oe7 oan5, chong2-si7 lan2 si5-siong5 teh khiam3-kheh kang-lang5. Na7 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 si5-tai7 pi2-kau3, kin-a2-jit8 lan2 e5 jin5-khau2 si7 ke-thiN, chong2-si7 choe3 kang e5 chin chio2. Sou2-i2 lan2 tioh8 ke3-siok8 iau3-kiu5 chheng-lian5 lam5-lu2 chi3-goan7 lai5 choe3 soan-kau3 e5 kang-chok, lan2 su-iau3 koh-khah choe7 e5 kang-lang5.

Te7 5----In-ui7 lan2 bo5 oh8 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat.

Ti7 The5-mou5-thai3 hou7-su 2 chiuN 2 chat, lan2 oe7 thang khoaN3-kiN3 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat: 몮Li2 ti7 choe7-choe7 kan-cheng3 e5 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 sou2 tui3 goa2 thiaN-kiN3 chiah e5 su7, tioh8 kau-thok tiong-sin3 e5 lang5, chiong-lai5 kham-tit ka3-si7 pat8 lang5 e5.몯 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat si7 ka3-si7 pat8-lang5, ia7 kio3 siu7 ka3-si7 e5 lang5 tioh8 koh-chai3 ka3-si7 pat8-lang5; in-ui7 kang-lang5 siu7-hun3 liau2 chhut-khi3 kang-chok, koh khi3 hun3-lian7 pat8 e5 kang-lang5.

Kim-jit7 choe3 ho2 e5 hong-hoat si7 khai-pan7 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7, hun3-lian7 hap8-eng7 e5 kang-lang5. In keng-koe3 hun3-lian7 liau2-au7 chiu7 thang chhe-phai3, tui3 ka-ki7 e5 lang5 thoan5 hok-im si7 choe3 ho2 e5 hong-hoat, lan2 bo5 kho2-leng5 kan-taN kho3 goa7-kok soan-kau3-su tui3 choan5 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im, in-ui7 lang5-giah8 bo5 kau3-giah8.

Li2 oe7 ki3-tit Ia5-sou tai7-seng u7 hun3-lian7 12 e5 hak8-seng, chong2-si7 au7-lai5 u7 hun3-lian7 70 e5. Po2-lo5 bo5 choe3 bok8-su, i hou7 lang5 hoan2-hoe2, ka7 in siat-lip8 tiuN2-lo2 liau2-au7 chiu7 koh khi3 pat8 sou2-chai7. I hou7 pun2 toe7 e5 leng2-to7-chia2 hu7-chek kau3-hoe7, hou7 in ka-ki7 chi-chhi5, in-ui7 si7 oah8 e5, ia7 oah8 e5 tek-khak oe7 tiong2-toa7.

Ti7 Su3-tou5 heng5-toan7 19 chiuN 8-10, 18-20 chat, lan2 oe7-thang tit-tioh8 ki5-biau7 e5 bou5-hoan7. Lan2 chiah ti7 te2-te2 e5 2 ni5 ku2, sio2 A-se-a e5 lang5 long2 i2-keng thiaN tioh8 hok-im. Chin choe7 siok8 ti7 sia5-sut8 e5 chheh long2 ti7 cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 eng7 hoe2 sio, hit-si5 sou2 sio e5 chheh, ke3-tat8 kui2 na7 chheng khou, ia7 ti7 hia to7-li2 toa7-toa7 tit-tioh8 heng-ong7.

Chit e5 su7 si7 chaiN2-iuN7 hoat-seng? Po2-lo5 me5-jit8 teh ka3 chheh, i pun2-sin tong-jian5 bo5 pian3-kiaN5 choan5 A-se-a, ti7 mui2 chit8 e5 siaN5-chhi7 thoan5-to7. I si5-siong5 tiam3 ti7 chit e5 sou2-chai7 ka3-si7 lang5, au7-lai5 tit-tioh8 ka3-si7 e5 lang5 chiah khi3 tak8 sou2-chai7 soan-thoan5 hok-im, hit e5 kiat-ko2 si7 ki3 ti7 Su3-tou5 heng5-toan7 19 chiuN. I bo5-lun7 khi3 ta2-loh8, chiu7-si7 몮kang2-to7 kap ka3-si7몯 (Su3-tou5 heng5-toan7 14 chiuN 21 chat) chit e5 hong-hoat m7-bian2 siu-kai2, tak8 sou2-chai7 long2 oe7-thang chiau3 an2-ni choe3.

Se In3-tou7 Soan-to7-hoe7 i2-keng cheng3-beng5 chit e5 hoan-tou7. In ti7 Kou2-pa u7 siat-lip8 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7, mui2 chit8 keng e5 kau3-hoe7 chiu7-si7 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7, jian5-au7 ia7 kau3 ti7 Hai2-te7, au7-lai5 ti7 To-beng5-ni5-ka Kiong7-ho5-kok, kap Ge5-be2-ka ia7 siat-lip8 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7, hian7-chai7 in ti7 Hoat-siok8 e5 chit8 e5 to2-su7 choe3 te7 5 pai2 siang7 khoan2 e5 kang-chok. An2-ni choe3 e5 kiat-ko2 chaiN2-iuN7? Tui3 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7 chhut-lai5 e5 chin choe7 hak8-seng, long2 kai3 ti7 Se In3-tou7 tak8 e5 hai2-su7, ia7 i2-keng tit-tioh8 8 ban7 goa7 mia5 e5 lang5 kui Chu2 lah.

Koe3-khi3 kui2 na7 10 ni5 e5 tiong-kan, lan2 sou2 eng7 e5 hong-hoat si7 siat-lip8 kau3-hoe7 ti7 toa7 siaN5-chhi7. Chong2-si7 tiam3 ti7 phian-phiah sou2-chai7 e5 lang5, long2 bo5 thiaN-tioh8 hok-im, ia7 bo5 ki-hoe7 thang thiaN-kiN3 Se In3-tou7 Soan-to7-hoe7 u7 chhai2-iong7 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat, hian7-chai7 mui2-ni5 ni5-hoe7 e5 gi7-oan5 u7 chhiau-koe3 7 chheng lang5 i2-siong7, ti7 hia Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 chin kin2 thoan5 chhut-khi3.

Ti7 Ai-the5-ou-pek, soan-kau3-su e5 kang-chok chi2-u7 tam7-poh8 e5 chin3-tian2 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 khi3 in hia e5 si5, sin3-chia2 hui-siong5 chio2, chong2-si7 ti7 I2-tai7-li7 lang5 chiam3-nia2 e5 si5, in pun2-toe7 e5 lang5 lai5 chiap-soa3 thoan5-to7 e5 kang; sui-jian5 chin choe7 lang5 siu7 koaiN ti7 kaN-lo5, siu7 piN-phah koh choe3 sun5-kau3-chia2, chong2-si7 u7 in2-chhoa7 2 ban7 lang5 kau3 Ki-tok e5 bin7-cheng5 lai5, ia7 chiah e5 kang-chok bo5 chit8 e5 soan-kau3-su chham-ka, hian7-chai7 ti7 hia u7 5 ban7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, 300 keng pun2-toe7 kau3-hoe7, che si7 ki5-biau7 e5 sin5-jiah ah! Chit e5 hong-hoat si7 choe3 li2-siong2 e5 hong-hoat, che si7 beh chin chiaN3 seng5-kong chi2-u7 chit8 e5 hong-hoat.

Chit khoan2 e5 hong-hoat ia7 seng2 chin choe7 hui3-iong7, oe7 thang tui3 in e5 kau3-hoe7 tit-tioh8 chi-chhi5. Au7-lai5 it-chhe3 e5 kang-chok chiu7 oe7 chiaN5-choe3 ka-ki7 chi-chhi5 e5 kang-chok, chiu7-si7 chu7-thoan5, chu7-ti7, chu7-kip. Che si7 Seng3-keng e5 hong-hoat, ia7 si7 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat, bo5 su-iau3 tioh8 kai2-chin3 e5.

Te7 6 ---- In-ui7 lan2 bo5 sin3, iN7-pang long2 tim5-lun5.

Siat-su2 chi2-u7 hiah e5 beng5-beng5 teh ku7-choat8 Ia5-sou e5 lang5 it-teng7 oe7 biat8-bo5, pat8-lang5 long2 oe7 tit-kiu3, lan2 chiu7 bo5 pit-iau3 ka7 in kong2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 su7. Chong2-si7 Seng3-keng u7 ka3-si7, kiN3-na7 bo5 sin3 e5 lang5 chiu7-si7 tim5-lun5 e5, in chi2-u7 ti7 hok-im e5 lai7-bin7 chiah u7 tit-kiu3 e5 ng3-bang7.

Po2-lo5 ti7 i2-ha7 kui2 ku3 oe7 e5 tiong-kan u7 teh kong2-khi2 koan-he7 iN7-pang e5 su7. 몮Koh lin2 peng5-sou3 tui3 lin2 e5 ke3-sit lin2 e5 choe7-koa3 lai5 si2 e5, seng-seng5 si7 choe3 thang siu7-khi3 e5, bo5 sou2 ng3-bang7, tiam3 ti7 se3-kan m7-bat Siong7-te3.몯 (I2-hut-sou2 2 chiuN, 1, 3, 12 chat) Che si7 in e5 cheng5-heng5, in si7 boe7 thang ban2 kiu3 e5, ia7 si7 eng2-oan2 tim5-lun5 e5.

Chia u7 2 toaN7 iau3-kin2 e5 Seng3-keng chat, te7 it ku3 si7 Su3-tou5 heng5-toan7 4 chiuN 12 chat, 몮Koh ti7 pat8 e5 peng7-bo5 chin2-kiu3; in-ui7 ti7 thiN-e7, bo5 siuN2-su3 pat8 e5 mia5 ti7 lang5 e5 tiong-kan, hou7 lan2 tiam3 ti7 i lai5 tit-kiu3.몯 In e5 sin5, in e5 chong-kau3 long2 bo5 lou7-eng7, Bok8-han2-bek-tek, Khong2-chu2, Sek-khia i2-kip8 ki5-thaN, long2 bo5 lou7-eng7, chi2-u7 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok, thang tit-kiu3. Te7 2 toaN7 e5 Seng3-keng chat si7 Iok-han7 14 chiuN 6 chat, Ia5-sou kong2, 몮Na7 bo5 tui3 goa2, chiu7 bo5 lang5 chiu7-kin7 Pe7.몯 Bo5 ki5-thaN e5 lou7 thang kau3 Siong7-te3 hia, I kong2: 몮Goa2 chiu7-si7 lou7몯, bo5 lang5 oe7 chiaN5 choe3 lou7, ia7 bo5 lang5 si7 lou7. Siat-su2 iN7-pang na7 si7 bo5 tim5-lun5, an2-ni chit 2 toaN7 e5 Seng3-keng tui3 in chiu7 bo5 sim2-mih8 i3-su3.

Chong2-si7 li2 kiam2-chhai2 beh kong2 an2-ni bo5 kong-to7, li2 siuN7 chit8 e5 thiaN3 e5 Siong7-te3 m7 ai3 an2-ni choe3, Siong7-te3 chi2-u7 beh chin2-kiu3 lan2 na7-tiaN7? Siat-su2 si7 an2-ni, it-chhe3 chiu7 m7 si7 un-tian2, I put-ko3 si7 teh heng5 che3-bu7 na7-tiaN7. Lan2 goan5-lai5 m7 eng-kai tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8, sou2-i2 long2 si7 un-tian2.

Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, goa2 m7 chai I beh an2-choaN2 choe3, chong2-si7 goa2 chai I sou2 choe3 e5 su7 si7 choat8-tui3, bo5 chho3-gou7 e5. I beh choe3 kong-gi7 e5 su7, goa2 beh chiong it-chhe3 kau ti7 I e5 chhiu2 nih, kau3 soah-boe2 goa2 oe7 chai I sou2 choe3 e5 su7, goa2 beh oan5-choan5 tit-tioh8 moa2-chiok, sou2-i2 goa2 beh kong2, 몮I choe3 liau2 chin tioh8, goa2 na7 ti7 I e5 lip8-tiuN5, goa2 ia7 beh an2-ni choe3몯. Lan2 ia7 beh chan3-seng5 thiN-sai3 e5 i3-kain3 몮li2 e5 sim2-phoaN3 si7 chin-sit8 koh kong-gi7.몯 (Khe2-si7 liok8 16 chiuN 7 chat)

Te7 7 ---- M7-thang koh sit-pai7.

Lan2 long2 chin goan7-i3 kiaN5 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3, lan2 ia7 chai chiong to7-li2 thoan5-kau3 phou2-thiN-e7 i2-goa7, bo5 chit8-hang7 su7 thang hou7 I e5 sim boan2-chiok. Siat-su2 ti7 koe3-khi3 lan2 u7 sit-pai7, an2-ni lan2 ti7 chiong-lai5 chiu7 bo5 li2-iu5 thang koh chai3 sit-pai7. TaN lan2 tioh8 lai5 choe3 lan2 e5 kang, tioh8 chiau3 lan2 e5 tiau3-beng7 khai-si2 lai5 kang-chok. Tek-khak tioh8 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7. SiaN2-su7 bo5 beh ti7 lan2 e5 se3-tai7 oan5-seng5 nih?

Siong7-te3 teh kio3 li2, I ia7 chin ai3 li2 khi3. ChhiaN2 sun7-hok8 Seng3 sin5, m7 thang ui5-poe7 tui3 thiN lai5 e5 iN7-siong7, chhiaN2 in3 kong2: 몮Chu2 ah, goa2 ti7 chia, chhe goa2.몯 Kiam2-chhai2 I ai3 li2 tioh8 chhe-phai3 chit8-ui7 li2 e5 tai7-li2-chia2 khi3, na7 an2-ni, chhiaN2 li2 chin7-lat8 khi3 than3 chiN5; chong2-si7 tioh8 chiong chiN5 hong7-hian3, chhe-phai3 lang5 tai7-the3 li2, khi3 thoan5 hok-im, li2 tioh8 chin7 li2 e5 pun2-hun7 ti7 se3-kai3 e5 thoan5-to7. Kiam2-chhai2 si7 Siong7-te3 kio3 li2 tioh8 ki5-to2, m7 thang kou-hu7 I, tioh8 chiaN5-choe3 tai7-to2 e5 lang5, ti7 li2 e5 sim-lai7 tioh8 u7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 su7, ui7-tioh8 ti7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 hiah e5 lang5 ki5-to2, tioh8 ui7-tioh8 keng-hui3 ki5-to2, tioh8 bo5 theng5 e5 ki5-to2 tit8-kau3 choan5 se3-kai3 long2 tit-tioh8 hok-im.
 
Tu3-chia2 Su2-bit8-su Phok-su7, si7 hian7-tai7 chhut-mia5 e5 pou3-to7-ka, ia7 si7 iu-siu3 e5 chok-chia2. Siong7-te3 u7 siuN2-su3 i tui3 thiN lai5 e5 ti3-hui7, sou2-i2 i u7 sia2 20 goa7 pun2 e5 chheh. Chhin-chhiuN7 몮Chu2 beh koh lai5몯, chiu7-si7 i e5 tai7-piau2 chok-phin2. Ki5-thaN i ia7 u7 sia2 1000 goa7 siu2 e5 seng3-si. M7 na7 an2-ni Siong7-te3 ia7 siun2-su3 i chin toa7 e5 pou3-to7 un-su3, i e5 kha-jiah pian3-thoan5 ti7 se3-kai3 5 toa7 chiu. In-ui7 i sou2 thoan5 e5 hok-im si7 kan2-tan koh u7 toa7 kam2-tong7 lat8, sou2-i2 tui3 i sou2 thoan5 e5 hok-im lai5 chiap-lap8 Ki-tok e5 lang5, hui-siong5 choe7.

Siong7-te3 m7-na7 siun2-su3 i pou3-to7 kap sia2-chok e5 un-su3, ia7 tek8-piat8 eng7 i, lai5 chhong3-siat Ka-na2-tai7 To-lun5-to Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7. Tui3 ti7 i e5 bok8-hoe7, chit keng kau3-hoe7 kim-jit8 i2-keng chiaN5-choe3 choan5 se3-kai3 pou3-to7 e5 ki3-ho7. Hian7-si5 Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 u7 phai3 350 e5 soan-kau3-su, hun-soaN3 ti7 se3-kai3 tak8 sou2-chai7, ti7 40 goa7 e5 thoan5-the2 teh thoan5 hok-im.

Su2 Phok-su7 hian7-chai7 si7 choan-jim7 cho3 Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 pou3-to7 bok8-su, kau3-hoe7 e5 su7 kau-tai3 i e5 kiaN2 Su2 Po2-lo5 bok8-su teh siat-hoat. Siang7-si5 Su2 Phok-su7 ia7 kiam-jim7 choe3 Se3-kai3 Bun5-ji7 Pou3-to7 Hiap8-hoe7 Beng5-u7 Hoe7-tiuN2, hou7 chit e5 hoe7 tit-tioh8 chin toa7 e5 pang-chan7, goan7 Siong7-te3 jit8-jit8 ke-thiN su3-hok i e5 kang-chok.

